description:
This Winter Gray Metallic 2014 Toyota Prius Two is a great choice! Check out the following: No Accidents! One Owner! City 51/Hwy 48 Carpet Floor Mats ($225 value)
  • Includes front and rear carpeted floor mats, and cargo mat.
WINTER GRAY METALLIC, DARK GRAY, FABRIC SEAT TRIM Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
  • Proximity key with keyless entry and push button start - Now close counts in horseshoes and car handles. You know you have your keys on you, but where exactly you're not sure. There's no need to dig around for them. Thanks to Proximity key with keyless entry and push button start you can get in and get going, all with your keys safe and sound - wherever that is...
  • Proximity key with keyless entry and push button start - Now close counts in horseshoes and car handles. You know you have your keys on you, but where exactly you're not sure. There's no need to dig around for them. Thanks to Proximity key with keyless entry and push button start you can get in and get going, all with your keys safe and sound - wherever that is...
In-car Entertainment
  • Touchscreen - flat out convenient. Say goodbye to the twists and turns of your daily drive...we're talking about buttons and knobs of course! Touchscreen allows you to control certain features with your fingertips, making it easy to use while also providing information at a glance. With touchscreen, your fingerprints will be all over your drive.
  • Wireless audio streaming - Strike the cord. With wireless streaming, the endless library of music on your mobile device is available through your vehicle's sound system! Make a playlist befitting of your road trip as it rolls along, let the back seat passengers control the selection, catch up on your favorite podcasts. With wireless audio streaming, all you have to do is press play.
Powertrain and Mechanical
  • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
  • Inline-4 engines produce adequate horsepower while typically offering better fuel efficiency and more economical maintenance than larger engines.
Safety and Security
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
  • Ignition immobilizer - Theft is a non-starter. You can feel more secure about your vehicle being there when you come back. Ignition immobilizer is a passive security system consisting of a transmitter in the ignition key and a sensor located in the vehicle. If both are not present or do not recognize each other, the vehicle will not start. Ignition immobilizer a sure-fire way to prevent the theft of your vehicle.
Technology and Telematics
  • Wireless connectivity - Strike the cord. Wireless technology makes it easy to place calls without having to fumble with your phone. It integrates your device with the system inside your vehicle for hands-free access. Keep connected and keep your hands on the wheel with wireless connectivity.
To be sure you don't miss out, give us a call at and schedule a test drive. We are located at 2207 North Belt Highway Saint Joseph MO 64506. We look forward to seeing you soon!

description: Meet your future frugal friend: a pristine 2007 Toyota Prius One in Super White with a Dark Gray cloth interior — the automotive equivalent of a sensible cardigan that somehow still gets compliments. Under the hood (well, under the small bonnet) is Toyota’s famous Hybrid Synergy Drive pairing a 1.5L Hybrid I4 (76 hp, 82 ft-lbs torque from the gasoline engine) with electric assist and an electronically controlled continuously variable transmission (ECVT). Translation: silent creep in EV mode, smooth acceleration, and regenerative braking that harvests energy every time you pretend to be aggressive in traffic but actually lift off the gas. Factory-standard features (the stuff it rolled off the assembly line with, not aftermarket gizmos): - Hybrid Synergy Drive system with regenerative braking, EV mode capability, and eco-minded engineering to squeeze maximum MPG from every commute. - Center-mounted multi-information display showing instantaneous and average fuel economy, hybrid energy flow, trip information and range — perfect for the nerd who loves watching numbers drop into the green zone. - Efficient heating and ventilation with manual A/C controls and a comfortable Dark Gray cloth interior that’s easy to live with and surprisingly forgiving of coffee threats. - AM/FM radio with a single-disc CD player and auxiliary inputs for your music stash (no Bluetooth sorcery required). - Power windows, power door locks and remote keyless entry — because fumbling for keys is so 2006. - Tilt steering wheel and cruise control for highway zen. - 60/40 split-folding rear seats to expand cargo space when impulse Ikea runs or weekend-errand heroics call. - 15-inch wheels with wheel covers, rear hatch with wiper, and a compact, practical cargo area — the small-but-capable hybrid hatch formula. - Safety systems include antilock brakes (ABS) with electronic brake-force distribution, traction control and Toyota’s suite of airbags (front and front-seat side airbags plus side curtain protection), plus child-seat LATCH anchors — proof this car is more responsible than most of us on a Monday morning. This particular Prius has clocked under 61,000 miles — that’s averaging less than 4,000 miles per year — so it’s been driven like a well-behaved pensioner rather than an aspiring rally car. Fuel economy is the real headline: EPA-ish numbers of about 48 MPG city and 45 MPG highway, which means fewer stops for gas and more stops for snacks instead. Cosmetically and mechanically this Prius is in excellent overall condition — clean exterior Super White paint, tidy Dark Gray cloth cabin, and the sort of low-mileage demeanor that makes you feel like you found a unicorn that runs on electricity and common sense. If you want a dependable, economical, slightly smug-looking hybrid that laughs silently at the gas pump, this Prius is waiting — and it won’t complain if you play the radio too loudly. CAR PLUS FINANCE 17281 Beach Boulevard Suite 102 Huntington Beach, CA 92647 (310) 539-2888

With its 2.0L 4-cylinder engine, 6-speed automatic transmission, and impressive fuel efficiency of 28 city/38 highway MPG, this Focus delivers a rewarding and economical driving experience. The sleek green exterior complements the well-appointed interior, creating a stylish and practical package.

Beyond the impressive performance and efficiency, this Focus also offers a wealth of convenience and safety features. The Convenience Package and Equipment Group 201A provide thoughtful amenities like cruise control, map lights, and a perimeter alarm, while the array of airbags, stability control, and other advanced safety systems give you peace of mind on the road.

Whether you're looking for a commuter car, a versatile runabout, or a reliable daily driver, this 2012 Ford Focus SE deserves a closer look. With its blend of practicality, technology, and style, it's a compelling option that could be the perfect fit for your driving needs.

We invite you to come in and experience this Focus for yourself. Take it for a test drive and see how it handles the roads. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and help you find the right vehicle to meet your needs.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and practicality in this 2017 Hyundai Elantra GT Base. With its sleek exterior design, spacious interior, and impressive array of features, this compact hatchback is the ideal choice for the savvy driver seeking a versatile and well-equipped vehicle.

• 6 Speakers

• CD player

• Air Conditioning
• Rear window defroster
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Speed-sensing steering
• Traction control
• 4-Wheel Disc Brakes

Powered by a 2.0L DOHC engine and paired with a 6-Speed Automatic with Shiftronic transmission, this Elantra GT delivers a smooth and efficient driving experience. With an EPA-estimated 24 city/32 highway MPG, you'll enjoy exceptional fuel economy for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Step inside and discover the well-appointed cabin, featuring premium cloth seating surfaces, a split-folding rear seat, and an array of convenient amenities. The Elantra GT's spacious interior and versatile cargo area make it the perfect companion for your active lifestyle, whether you're hauling equipment, transporting bulky items, or simply enjoying the ride.

Equipped with a comprehensive suite of safety features, including dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, and electronic stability control, this Elantra GT prioritizes your protection on the road. Additionally, the vehicle's sleek exterior design, featuring a body-color bumper and a rear spoiler, adds a touch of modern sophistication.

Don't miss the opportunity to experience the exceptional value and driving dynamics of this 2017 Hyundai Elantra GT Base. Schedule a test drive today and discover why this compact hatchback is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

Customer must take delivery of the vehicle and execute all California required documentation at BMW of Santa Monica. We reserve the right to revise price, equipment, mileage, and certification status as a result of changing market conditions, manufacturer/distributor notices including recall notices, or errors. All vehicle pricing expires upon close of business the same day. The stock images shown are for illustration purposes only and are not an exact representation of the actual vehicle. Experience the future of driving with this sleek and eco-friendly 2017 BMW i3 C, now available at BMW of Santa Monica. This one-owner vehicle (stock number L103, VIN WBY1Z8C56HV889237) boasts a striking Mineral Gray exterior with BMW i Frozen Blue accents, perfectly complemented by a sophisticated Mega Carum Spice Gray interior.

With just 23,935 miles on the odometer, this i3 C is ready for many more adventures. Powered by a 0.7L electric motor paired with an automatic transmission, this hybrid vehicle offers an exhilarating yet efficient driving experience. The rear-wheel-drive configuration ensures dynamic handling, while the electric power-assist speed-sensing steering provides precise control.

Step inside and discover a world of comfort and technology. The heated front seats offer warmth on chilly days, while the automatic air conditioning keeps you comfortable year-round. The leather steering wheel adds a touch of luxury to your daily commute. The integrated navigation system and smart device integration keep you connected and on course, while the HD Radio and SiriusXM Satellite Radio (with a 1-year AllAccess subscription) provide endless entertainment options.

Safety is paramount in the BMW i3 C, featuring a comprehensive airbag system, including dual-stage front airbags, side-impact airbags, and curtain airbags for both rows. The vehicle is equipped with electronic stability control, ABS, and driveline traction control for enhanced stability in various driving conditions. Rear parking sensors make maneuvering in tight spaces a breeze.

Charging is convenient with multiple options: a 7.4 kW onboard charger allows for a full charge in 28 hours at 110/120V, 4.5 hours at 220/240V, or just 0.7 hours at 440V. The lithium-ion traction battery boasts a 33 kWh capacity, ensuring ample range for your daily needs.

The exterior features 19-inch light alloy turbine wheels (Style 429) with all-season tires, adding to the vehicle's futuristic aesthetic. The power-folding side mirrors with integrated turn signals and auto-dimming function on the driver's side enhance both safety and convenience.

Inside, you'll find a user-friendly interface with two LCD monitors in the front, providing access to various vehicle functions and information. The 50-50 folding rear seat offers flexibility for cargo transportation, while the rigid cargo cover keeps your belongings out of sight.

Additional features include a garage door transmitter, cruise control, proximity key for doors and push-button start, and three 12V DC power outlets. The BMW Assist eCall Emergency SOS capability provides peace of mind in case of emergencies.

Don't miss this opportunity to own a piece of BMW's innovative electric future. Visit BMW of Santa Monica today and take this 2017 BMW i3 C for a test drive – your eco-friendly adventure awaits!

Vehicle Details
2015 Nissan Rogue SL FWD – 4-Cylinder 2.5L, Gadsden AL This 2015 Nissan Rogue SL with a fuel-efficient 2.5L 4-cylinder engine and smooth automatic transmission offers exceptional value, currently priced as the best deal in Gadsden, AL. The SL trim brings premium comfort and advanced technology to this compact crossover, delivering a refined driving experience whether commuting or on weekend trips. Inside, Automatic Climate Control maintains a comfortable cabin temperature while the BOSE stereo system provides rich, immersive sound for every drive. The back-up camera enhances parking confidence and safety, giving you a clear view when reversing into tight spots. Lane Departure Warning adds an extra layer of protection by alerting you if the vehicle begins to drift, helping promote attentive driving on busy roads and highways. XM Radio keeps you entertained with a wide variety of channels and on-demand content for long drives. This Nissan Rogue combines a roomy interior, versatile cargo capacity, and user-friendly features that meet the needs of families and individuals seeking reliability and style. With its proven 4-cylinder powertrain and FWD efficiency, this vehicle balances performance and economy. Located in Gadsden, AL, this Nissan Rogue SL represents the best-priced opportunity to own a well-equipped crossover—schedule a test drive today and experience its comfort, technology, and value firsthand.

Equipment
The leather seats in this Nissan Rogue are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. with XM/Sirus Satellite Radio you are no longer restricted by poor quality local radio stations while driving this model. Anywhere on the planet, you will have hundreds of digital stations to choose from. The vehicle's Lane Departure Warning keeps you safe by alerting you when you drift from your lane. You'll never again be lost in a crowded city or a country region with the navigation system on this small suv. This unit's Forward Collision Warning system alerts the driver to potential front-end collisions, enhancing safety. Protect the vehicle from unwanted accidents with a cutting edge backup camera system. This small suv keeps you comfortable with Auto Climate. Engulf yourself with the crystal clear sound of a BOSE sound system in this small suv. The Nissan Rogue features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system.

Packages
SL Premium Package: Blind Spot Warning, Lane Departure Warning, Power Panoramic Moonroof, LED Headlights with Auto Levelizer, Forward Collision Warning. Splash Guards. Chrome Rear Bumper Protector. **Equipment listed is based on original vehicle build and subject to change. Please confirm the accuracy of the included equipment by calling the dealer prior to purchase.**

Additional Information

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2025 Subaru Outback Premium. This versatile SUV seamlessly blends style, capability, and advanced technology, making it the perfect companion for your adventures.

Highlighted features include:
• Blind Spot Detection (BSD) & Rear Cross Traffic Alert (RCTA)
• Keyless Access with Push-Button Start
• Subaru 11.6" Multimedia System with Navigation
• Automatic Temperature Control
• Hands-Free Power Rear Gate
• Power Moonroof

The Outback's 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC engine, paired with Subaru's legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 26 city/32 highway MPG.

Step inside and be captivated by the premium cabin, featuring plush cloth upholstery and a wealth of thoughtful amenities. The 11.6-inch multimedia system with navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained on the go. The Hands-Free Power Rear Gate and Keyless Access with Push-Button Start add a touch of convenience to your daily routine.

Safety is paramount in the Outback, with features like Blind Spot Detection, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, and a suite of advanced airbags providing you and your passengers with peace of mind. The Subaru EyeSight Driver Assist Technology, including Adaptive Cruise Control, further enhances your driving experience.

BSD W/RCTA & KEYLESS ACCESS & PUSH BUTTON START, CRIMSON RED PEARL, SLATE BLACK, CLOTH UPHOLSTERY, SPLASH GUARDS, REAR BUMPER COVER, LED UPGRADE, ALL-WEATHER FLOOR LINERS Safety and Security
  • With this system the driver's hands must remain on the wheel at all times but can be removed briefly (for a few seconds), otherwise the vehicle will prompt the driver to put their hands back on the wheel.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display. The camera is equipped with its own washer.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay and Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring

Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2024 MINI John Cooper Works Clubman. This exceptional vehicle combines exhilarating performance, head-turning style, and an array of premium features that will captivate your senses.

Meticulously maintained and MINI Certified, this Clubman boasts an impressive list of sought-after amenities, including:

• MINI CERTIFIED
• ICONIC TRIM

• Dynamic Digital Instrument Cluster

• harman/kardon® Premium Sound System
• MINI Excitement Package
• Power Front Seats
• Piano Black Exterior Trim

The MINI Certified Pre-Owned program ensures your peace of mind, offering a comprehensive 197-point inspection, 12-month/unlimited mile limited warranty, and 24/7 roadside assistance. With a $0 deductible and a transferable warranty, you can take to the road with confidence.

Meticulously maintained and brimming with premium features, this 2024 MINI John Cooper Works Clubman is a true driver's delight. Experience the exceptional craftsmanship, thrilling performance, and unparalleled style that make this Clubman a standout in its class. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this MINI can elevate your driving experience.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and technology in the 2024 Subaru Outback Limited. This versatile SUV is designed to elevate your driving experience, offering a seamless combination of rugged performance and refined sophistication.

Highlighted features include:
• Power Moonroof & Heated Steering Wheel & Navigation System
• Radio: Subaru STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Navigation System
• Automatic Temperature Control
• Power Driver Seat
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls
• Power Moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Fully Automatic Headlights
• DriverFocus (Driver Monitoring System)
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Heated Front Bucket Seats
• Perforated Leather-Trimmed Upholstery

Powered by a 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine with Lineartronic CVT and Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, the Outback Limited delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 26 city/32 highway MPG. This SUV's rugged capability is further enhanced by its generous ground clearance, making it equally at home on the open road or the less-traveled path.

Step inside the Outback Limited and experience the epitome of modern luxury. The spacious interior is adorned with premium materials, including perforated leather-trimmed upholstery and a heated steering wheel, ensuring your comfort on every journey. The advanced Subaru STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Navigation System, complete with wireless smartphone integration, provides seamless connectivity and intuitive controls, keeping you connected and entertained.

Safety is also a top priority in the Outback Limited, with features like the DriverFocus Distraction Mitigation System, which monitors driver alertness, and a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies to help keep you and your loved ones protected.

Whether you're embarking on a weekend adventure or navigating the daily commute, the 2024 Subaru Outback Limited is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and technology that this exceptional SUV has to offer. Schedule a test drive today and discover the Outback Limited's exceptional value.

Elevate your driving experience with the Outback Touring XT's premium features, including heated and ventilated front seats, a power liftgate, and a panoramic moonroof. The Nappa leather-trimmed upholstery and heated steering wheel add a touch of luxury to every journey.

Built for adventure, combining rugged capability with Subarus proven Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive. Powered by a turbocharged Boxer engine paired with a smooth automatic transmission, the Outback Wilderness delivers confident acceleration, enhanced off-road capability, and dependable performance on pavement, dirt, and snow. Unique Wilderness tuning, increased ground clearance, and all-terrain styling set it apart from the standard Outback lineup.

Inside, the cabin is designed with durability and comfort in mind, featuring water-repellent StarTex upholstery, heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a large touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The interior offers ample passenger space, flexible cargo capacity, and thoughtful storage solutions, making it ideal for outdoor enthusiasts and daily drivers alike.

This Outback Wilderness comes with Lifetime Coverage, providing added long-term value and peace of mind beyond the factory warranty. CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED, WILDERNESS, APPLE CARPLAY, POWER MOONROOF, HEATED FRONT AND REAR SEATS, ONE-OWNER

Adventure ready and city smart, this 2022 Subaru Outback Wilderness in Ice Silver Metallic is built for drivers who want more capability without giving up comfort. With a clean CARFAX, one-owner history, recent factory service, and Subaru Certified Pre-Owned status, this Outback Wilderness stands out as a confident choice for everything from weekday commutes to weekend trailheads. Its rugged styling, turbocharged power, and thoughtful upgrades make it a vehicle that truly lives up to its name.

As a Certified Pre-Owned Subaru, this Outback Wilderness delivers exceptional peace of mind from day one. Subarus CPO program includes a 7-year or 100,000-mile powertrain warranty from the original in-service date, a comprehensive 152-point inspection performed by factory trained technicians, and roadside assistance for added confidence wherever the road leads. It is Subaru reliability, backed by Subaru, and designed to let you explore with confidence.

Powering this Wilderness is the responsive 2.4L DOHC turbocharged engine paired with Subarus Lineartronic CVT and legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive. With 22 city and 26 highway MPG, you get strong performance without sacrificing efficiency. The Wilderness package adds increased ground clearance, rugged suspension tuning, all-terrain focused 17-inch aluminum alloy wheels, roof rack, splash guards, and protective cladding, making this Outback especially capable when conditions get rough. Steering wheel paddle shifters and X-Mode capability keep you in control on everything from snow to gravel.

Inside, the cabin balances durability with refinement. StarTex-trimmed upholstery is both comfortable and easy to clean, while heated front and rear seats, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a power moonroof keep everyone comfortable year round. The massive Subaru STARLINK 11.6-inch Multimedia Navigation system anchors the dash with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, SiriusXM capability, and wireless charging. Thoughtful touches like the power liftgate, HomeLink garage transmitter, auto-dimming mirrors, rear seat back protector, and cargo sidewall protection make everyday use effortless.

Safety and driver assistance are front and center with features like adaptive cruise control, reverse automatic braking, rear view camera, electronic stability control, brake assist, and Subaru STARLINK Safety and Security. With its strong safety reputation and award winning residual value, the Outback Wilderness continues to be one of the most trusted adventure vehicles on the road.

When you purchase from Carter Subaru Ballard, you are choosing a dealership that has earned the trust of generations as Seattles trusted Subaru dealership since 1960. Every Subaru owner here also enjoys our exclusive Loan Cars for Life program, a benefit that adds real long-term value well beyond the sale. It is just one more reason so many drivers return to Carter Subaru Ballard again and again.

This Certified Pre-Owned 2022 Outback Wilderness is ready to take you wherever curiosity leads next. Call us today at (206) 782-7475, visit www.cartersubaruballard.com
, or stop by our showroom to see it in person. Vehicles this well equipped and this well cared for do not stay available for long. Come shop at Carter Subaru Today!

description: This Black 2020 Chevrolet Equinox LS 2WD offers a smart blend of comfort, efficiency, and everyday practicality, making it an excellent choice for commuting, family travel, or daily errands. With its modern design, spacious interior, and dependable performance, the Equinox continues to be one of Chevrolet\'s most popular compact SUVs. Under the hood, the Equinox LS is powered by a fuel-efficient 1.5L turbocharged 4-cylinder engine paired with a smooth automatic transmission. The 2-wheel-drive (2WD) configuration delivers a comfortable ride and excellent fuel economy, ideal for highway driving and city use. Steering is responsive, and the suspension provides a quiet, well-controlled driving experience. Inside, the cabin is thoughtfully designed with comfort and functionality in mind. The Equinox LS features cloth seating, a power-adjustable driver seat, air conditioning, power windows and locks, cruise control, and a spacious layout that comfortably seats both passengers and cargo. The rear seats fold flat, allowing for expanded storage space when needed. Technology features include a touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth connectivity, USB ports, and steering-wheel-mounted audio controls. The backup camera provides added confidence when reversing or parking, making daily driving easier and safer. Safety remains a priority with Chevrolet\'s standard safety technologies, including stability control, traction control, lane keep assist, forward collision alert, automatic emergency braking, and multiple airbags. These features work together to help protect you and your passengers on every drive. The exterior is finished in a sleek black paint that gives the Equinox a clean, modern look. Stylish body lines, a bold front grille, and alloy wheels complete the appearance, making this SUV both practical and visually appealing. With its reputation for reliability, low operating costs, and comfortable ride quality, this 2020 Chevrolet Equinox LS 2WD is a smart choice for drivers seeking a dependable SUV with modern technology and everyday versatility. Price does not include $0 processing fee

  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.

Trusted Name for 60+ Years Serving our community for over six decades with integrity, quality, & customer satisfaction The Hansel Auto Group story begins in 1851. Joseph Hansel first entered the transportation industry selling horse-drawn carriages. Joseph's son continued to build the Hansel name, opening the family's first automotive dealership in 1901. Hansel Auto Group first expanded into the Sonoma Valley in 1961 under the leadership of Walter Hansel. Walter believed that the Hansel name was about more than just selling cars. description:
This 2024 Kia Soul LX is a versatile and practical compact hatchback that combines distinctive styling, efficient performance, and everyday usability. With 55,886 miles, this Soul has been moderately driven and remains a dependable choice for buyers seeking a late-model vehicle with strong reliability and value. Its exterior, finished in KDT (a contemporary, neutral tone), paired with a Black interior, gives the vehicle a clean and modern look suitable for a variety of lifestyles.

The Souls exterior design is instantly recognizable, featuring a boxy profile and upright stance that maximize interior space while maintaining a compact footprint. Its four-door hatchback layout ensures convenient access for passengers and cargo, while the compact dimensions make city driving and tight parking spaces effortless. The styling is modern yet practical, with subtle design cues that give it character without being overbearing.

Inside, the Black interior offers a functional and comfortable cabin environment. The seats are supportive and well-suited for daily commutes as well as longer drives, and the interior layout is intuitive, with controls positioned for ease of use. Despite its compact exterior, the Soul makes excellent use of space, providing ample headroom and legroom for front and rear passengers alike.

On the road, the front-wheel-drive configuration delivers predictable handling and a composed ride. The suspension is tuned to absorb everyday road imperfections, ensuring comfort for both driver and passengers. Steering is light and responsive, making maneuvering through traffic or parking straightforward. Its efficient powertrain also contributes to lower fuel costs, making it a practical choice for everyday driving.

Cargo versatility is a strong feature of the Soul LX. The rear hatch provides easy access to a generous cargo area that can accommodate groceries, luggage, or recreational gear. Folding the rear seats allows for additional cargo capacity when needed, making the vehicle adaptable to various lifestyle demands.

Overall, the 2024 Kia Soul LX is an excellent option for buyers seeking a practical, reliable, and stylish compact hatchback. With its well-designed interior, versatile cargo space, and easy-to-drive nature, it provides a smart and enjoyable choice for commuters, small families, or anyone looking for dependable daily transportation.

CPO benefits

152-point inspection | 7yr/100,000mi powertrain from original in-service date | $0 deductible | roadside assistance | vehicle history | transferable warranty | SiriusXM 3-month trial | STARLINK 1-year trial

Performance

Symmetrical AWD and the 2.5L H-4 supply confident traction with smooth, responsive power. CVT with driver-selectable mode keeps revs calm for efficiency rated at 26/33 MPG.

Comfort & Convenience

Heated front seats, dual-zone climate, and a leather steering wheel make cold mornings easier. Keyless access with push-button start plus cruise control and a pass-through rear seat streamline daily errands.

Technology

Apple CarPlay and Android Auto connect maps, calls, and playlists for easy control on the go. Back-up camera, trip computer, Smart Device Integration, and telematics add helpful info at a glance.

Safety

Blind Spot Monitor and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert help with lane changes and backing. Adaptive Cruise Control with Lane Keep Assist, Driver Monitoring, Front Collision Mitigation, and a robust airbag suite add confidence.

Exterior & Interior

Oasis Blue Pearl paint stands out with LED headlights, Auto High Beam, fog lamps, and heated turn-signal mirrors. Rear spoiler, aluminum wheels, privacy glass, and durable cloth sport seats complete the RS vibe.

Driving Experience

Surefooted, quiet, and eager, it feels planted in rain and snow.

History Summary

Certified Pre-Owned. One Owner. No Open Recalls. Active Warranty.

Combines refined comfort with turbocharged performance and Subarus proven Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive. Inside, the cabin offers a premium experience with leather-trimmed seating, heated front and rear seats, a power-adjustable drivers seat, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a large touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration. The spacious interior provides excellent passenger comfort and flexible cargo capacity, making it ideal for daily commuting and longer road trips.

This Outback comes with Lifetime Coverage, providing added long-term value and peace of mind beyond the factory warranty. If you want a newer compact SUV that’s practical, comfortable, and actually enjoyable to drive, this 2024 Kia Soul EX checks the right boxes. It has a clean CARFAX, strong fuel economy, and the EX trim brings the upgrades people actually care about.

This Soul EX feels modern and well thought out, not basic. It’s easy to maneuver, easy to park, and surprisingly roomy inside, making it a great fit for commuting, errands, and everyday Wisconsin driving.

Key features include
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Heated front seats
• Power driver seat
• Power moonroof
• Navigation system
• Dual-zone automatic climate control
• Auto high-beam headlights
• Backup camera
• Heated mirrors
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Puddle lights and remote keyless entry

Fuel economy stays strong at an EPA-estimated 27 city and 33 highway MPG, keeping ownership costs low without giving up comfort.

This Soul is Kia Certified Pre-Owned, adding real peace of mind. Certification includes a 165-point inspection, 10-year or 100,000-mile powertrain limited warranty from the original in-service date, 12-month or 12,000-mile Platinum coverage, roadside assistance, rental car and trip interruption reimbursement, transferable warranty, and a low deductible.

If you’re cross-shopping a Honda HR-V, Toyota Corolla Cross, Hyundai Kona, or Nissan Kicks, the Soul stands out for interior space, ease of ownership, and warranty coverage.

At Ewald Kia of Oconomowoc, we keep the process simple and transparent. Family-owned since 1964, with vehicles selected because they make sense for real life and real budgets.

Ask about our trade-in bonus and free, no-obligation appraisal. Clean, certified Souls like this don’t sit long once buyers start comparing features.

This Crystal Black Silica beauty with Carbon Black leather trim was purchased in Kentucky from the widow of the elderly gentleman who bought it brand new. Equipped with Subaru’s legendary all-wheel drive and a 5-speed manual transmission, this WRX is an absolute blast to drive. This vehicle does have a few tasteful performance upgrades already in place, including an aftermarket exhaust, upgraded suspension, and cold air intake (exact brands unknown), and it runs and drives excellent. If you’ve been searching for a low-mile WRX wagon with a clean, one owner, accident free history, this one checks a lot of boxes. For more info on this little Subie, contact Kevin at Mashburn Motors. 2018 Subaru Outback Premium — AWD reliability meets versatile comfort in Charleston, WV. This well-maintained Subaru Outback pairs Subaru's proven 4-cylinder 2.5L gasoline engine with symmetrical all-wheel drive for confident handling in rain, snow, and mountain roads. CARFAX 1-Owner and CARFAX Clean Report provide peace of mind, confirming a responsible ownership history and meticulous care. Inside, Apple CarPlay brings seamless smartphone integration for navigation, music, and hands-free calls, while Automatic Climate Control keeps every drive comfortable no matter the season. The Back-Up Camera makes parking and reversing easier and safer, and the thoughtful interior layout offers generous cargo space for weekend gear, groceries, or a road-trip load. You'll appreciate the Premium trim's upgraded comfort and convenience features, combining practical utility with stylish touches. Whether commuting through Charleston or heading out for an Appalachian adventure, this Subaru Outback balances fuel-efficient performance with a smooth, composed ride. Regular maintenance and the clean CARFAX history mean you're getting value and dependability. Located in Charleston, WV, this 2018 Subaru Outback Premium is priced to move — the best price available for comparable models in the area. Don't miss a chance to own a versatile, well-documented Subaru that's ready for more miles. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and experience why the Subaru Outback remains a top choice for active drivers.

Equipment
with XM/Sirus Satellite Radio you are no longer restricted by poor quality local radio stations while driving the Subaru Outback. Set the temperature exactly where you are most comfortable in the Subaru Outback. The fan speed and temperature will automatically adjust to maintain your preferred zone climate.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of rugged capability and refined luxury in the 2023 Subaru Outback Limited AWD. This exceptional vehicle is more than just a reliable SUV - it's a gateway to endless adventures and uncompromising comfort.

Black Leather interior.

• Lifetime Oil Changes
• Carfax Accident Free
• Florida Driven
• Heated Seats
• Backup Camera
• Keyless Access w/Push Button Start
• Power Moonroof & HSW & Navigation System
• Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirror w/Approach Light

Beneath its sleek, silver exterior lies the heart of a true adventurer. The 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, paired with the seamless CVT Lineartronic transmission and Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, delivers an impressive blend of power and efficiency. With 26 city/32 highway MPG, you'll conquer the roads with confidence and ease.

But this Outback is more than just a capable performer - it's a sanctuary of modern technology and premium amenities. The 11.6" STARLINK Multimedia Navigation System, complete with a 576-watt harman/kardon® surround sound system, puts you in complete control of your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of wireless smartphone integration, voice-activated controls, and a stunning high-resolution display.

As you slide into the perforated leather-trimmed seats, you'll be enveloped in unparalleled comfort. The heated front and rear seats, along with the heated steering wheel, ensure you and your passengers stay cozy, no matter the weather. The power driver's seat with memory function allows you to find your perfect driving position with ease.

Safety is paramount in the 2023 Outback Limited. The DriverFocus Distraction Mitigation System and a suite of advanced safety features, including Eyesight® Driver Assist Technology, work tirelessly to keep you and your loved ones protected on the road.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or tackling the great outdoors, the 2023 Subaru Outback Limited AWD is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of capability, technology, and luxury. Call us for more information at 888-512-4787 or Text Us directly at 45555 today!

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2023 Subaru Outback Limited. This versatile SUV boasts an impressive array of features that seamlessly blend style, technology, and safety, making it the perfect companion for your adventures.

Highlighted features of this exceptional vehicle include:

• Collision Warning System
• Heated Seats
• Blind-Spot Monitors
• Lane Keeping Assist
• Backup Camera
• Keyless Access with Push Button Start
• Apple CarPlay
• Android Auto
• Power Moonroof

Beneath the bold, eye-catching exterior lies a powerful 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, paired with a smooth and efficient CVT Lineartronic transmission and Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system. With an impressive fuel economy of 26 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway, this Outback delivers exceptional performance and efficiency, making it an ideal choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Step inside and experience the refined comfort and advanced technology that set this Outback apart. The leather-trimmed interior, heated front and rear seats, and power-adjustable driver's seat provide a luxurious and personalized driving experience. The Subaru STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Navigation System, complete with wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

Safety is a top priority in the Outback, with features like the DriverFocus Driver Monitoring System, Blind-Spot Monitors, and Lane Keeping Assist providing an extra layer of protection for you and your loved ones. The Backup Camera and Collision Warning System further enhance your awareness and confidence behind the wheel.

With its impressive capabilities, exceptional features, and timeless design, this 2023 Subaru Outback Limited is the perfect blend of versatility and sophistication. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the quality, performance, and value this Outback has to offer.

description: ===== Used 2023 Subaru Outback Premium --- Versatile AWD Capability & Everyday Comfort =====This used 2023 Subaru Outback Premium is a well-rounded midsize SUV designed for year-round confidence, comfort, and practicality. With Subaru's legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, generous ground clearance, and a refined interior, the Outback is equally at home on daily commutes, road trips, and light off-road adventures.*Clean title**Original MSRP:* $33,320==== Recent Service ====Recently serviced and fully inspected, including completed pre-delivery and maintenance inspections, 70,000-mile service, fresh oil and filter change, engine air filter replacement, and tire rotation.==== Performance & Drivetrain ====Powered by a 2.5L DOHC SUBARU BOXER® engine paired with a Lineartronic® CVT and 8-speed manual shift mode, this Outback delivers smooth, efficient performance. Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, X-MODE® traction management, and 8.7 inches of ground clearance provide confident handling in all weather and road conditions.==== Exterior Highlights ====Exterior features include 17-inch alloy wheels with black machine-finish accents, LED fog lights, LED steering-responsive headlights with high beam assist, roof rails with integrated retractable crossbars, heated power mirrors with turn signals, and Subaru's rugged raised suspension design.==== Interior & Technology ====The interior is thoughtfully designed with dual-zone automatic climate control, heated front seats as part of the All-Weather Package, a leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift lever, and a 10-way power driver's seat with lumbar support. Rear-seat vents and a versatile 60/40 split-folding rear seatback enhance passenger comfort and cargo flexibility.Technology highlights include Subaru STARLINK® 11.6-inch Multimedia Plus touchscreen, wireless smartphone connectivity with Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto?, HD Radio, SiriusXM® (4-month trial), multiple USB ports, Bluetooth® connectivity, and advanced adaptive cruise control with lane centering.==== Safety ====Equipped with Subaru EyeSight® Driver Assist Technology, this Outback includes automatic emergency steering, adaptive cruise control, lane centering, blind spot detection with rear cross-traffic alert, rear vision camera with dynamic guidelines, brake assist, stability control, and a full suite of airbags for added peace of mind.==== Why Buy from Walser? ====At Walser, you'll enjoy Upfront Pricing and a transparent, no-pressure buying experience. Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2016 Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 4MATIC®. This stunning SUV boasts a refined 3.5L V6 DOHC 24V engine, paired with a seamless 7-Speed Automatic transmission and Mercedes-Benz's renowned 4MATIC® all-wheel-drive system, delivering a remarkable blend of power and efficiency.

Highlighted features include:
• 8 Speakers
• DVD-Audio
• Weather band radio
• Memory seat
• Power Front Seats w/Driver Memory
• Emergency communication system: mbrace2
• Overhead airbag
• Electronic Stability Control
• Security system
• Compass
• Garage door transmitter: Homelink
• Leather steering wheel
• MB-Tex Leatherette Seat Trim
• 19" 5-Spoke Wheels

The striking exterior of this GLE 350 4MATIC® is complemented by a well-appointed interior, featuring premium materials and thoughtful design elements that elevate the driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of a power liftgate, the versatility of a split-folding rear seat, and the comfort of heated front seats.

Safety is paramount, and this GLE 350 4MATIC® delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including anti-lock brakes, traction control, and a full complement of airbags to protect you and your passengers.

Whether you're commuting in the city or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2016 Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 4MATIC® is the perfect companion. Its exceptional performance, luxurious amenities, and advanced safety technologies make it a standout in the premium SUV segment.

We invite you to experience the exceptional craftsmanship and refined capabilities of this 2016 Mercedes-Benz GLE 350 4MATIC® for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can elevate your driving experience.

description:
In developing our founding commitment ( The Cardinale Way ), we selected key words that are as meaningful to you as they are to our mission. One of those is “relationship.” With every introduction, we are looking, not for a single transaction, but to “develop” a relationship with our customers...not just a good relationship, but an “outstanding” relationship that will outlast your car. Another key element is that “everybody wins”. In a time when most people believe winners create losers, we endeavor to satisfy everybody involved. It means knowing our product well and our customer even better. It means listening and caring and understanding that people buy their second-most expensive item from people they trust. Whether you are a car enthusiast, or you just need a reliable ride, the right car for you means buying exactly what you need and ideally what you want. Over forty years ago, we entered the automobile business driven by a passion for people, and recognizing cars as a “vehicle” for creating meaningful connections. We also understood that helping people select, purchase and finance one of the most important tools of your daily life is a valuable pursuit. Our priority is and has always been making sure your new or used-car buying experience is both satisfying and successful. Within the Cardinale Automotive Group, we know that satisfying a wide range of needs requires a diversity of quality cars. We offer new Audi, BMW, GMC, Harley Davidson, Hyundai, Mazda, Nissan, Toyota and Volkswagen cars, along with used cars, trucks and SUVs by top manufacturers. We are committed to helping you find the right car, assisting you in choosing the right financing options, and becoming your trusted automobile dealer. Our relationship begins with our introduction and continues through the purchase, the financing, the service of the car and beyond. We look forward to developing an outstanding relationship with you.

Check out this pre-owned 2016 Subaru Outback we recently got in. On almost any road condition, this Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium offers solid performance, reliability, and comfort. Why spend more money than you have to? This Subaru Outback will help you keep the extra money you'd normally spend on gas. Navigate through all the icky weather with ease in this AWD-equipped Subaru Outback, and even get non-stop traction for your non-stop lifestyle! In addition to the amazing traction control, you may even qualify for an insurance reduction with this AWD vehicle. Low, low mileage coupled with an exacting maintenance program make this vehicle a rare find. The easiest choice in purchasing your next vehicle is choosing one with a detailed history like this gently driven pre-owned vehicle. This Subaru Outback is beautiful and the interior is clean with virtually no flaws. The first thing anyone notices about your car is the paint job and this car's is near perfect. More information about the 2016 Subaru Outback: The genius of the Outback has always been its ability to straddle classifications, it helped create the crossover segment in the 1990s. As such, the Outback competes with family cars, SUVs and, of course, other crossover vehicles. With a base price just short of $25,000, the Outback should be affordable enough for families considering a new Camry or Accord. With better off-road credentials and a more usable luggage compartment, the Outback offers increased versatility over plain Jane family sedans. At the same time, the Subaru Outback offers the kind of fuel economy that most mid-sized SUVs struggle to match. Strengths of this model include fuel-efficient transmissions, good ground clearance, spacious interior, Versatility, and standard all-wheel drive

Why we use market based pricing?


We believe that today's used car buyers search the Internet to find the best value on the vehicle they want. Each search returns dozens, if not hundreds, of similar vehicles in their area to consider. Customers shorten this to a manageable list by ranking vehicles with the best price and mileage at the top. Because of this we utilize a software tool that show us where our inventory ranks on popular car shopping sites when searched and gives us the information we need to immediately adjust our prices and drive customers to our lot. We believe that Market Based Pricing aligns our cars best with what the consumer is looking for.

description:
Discover the pinnacle of Porsche engineering and performance with this exceptional 2022 911 GT3. Meticulously maintained and with just 10,556 miles, this stunning white sports car is a true testament to Porsche's commitment to excellence.

• Exclusive design elements including:
- Black with Guards Red stitching interior trim
- Satin black wheels with Guards Red lip
- Carbon fiber exterior mirror trim
- Bose surround sound system
- LED headlights in black with PDLS
- Aluminum pedals and footrest
- Rear Park Assist
- Chrono Package with lap trigger preparation
- Guards Red seat belts

This 911 GT3 is more than just a sports car - it's a work of art, engineered to deliver an unparalleled driving experience. Powered by a 4.0L H6 DOHC 24V engine producing an exhilarating 502 horsepower, paired with a lightning-fast 7-Speed Porsche Doppelkupplung (PDK) transmission, this GT3 will leave you breathless.

Handling is equally impressive, thanks to the adaptive suspension, four-wheel independent suspension, and speed-sensitive steering. Whether carving through winding roads or accelerating onto the highway, this 911 GT3 will captivate you with its exceptional agility and responsiveness.

Stepping inside, you'll be greeted by a driver-focused cockpit that seamlessly blends form and function. The 4-Way Sport Seats Plus, heated front seats, and Porsche Communication Management system ensure both comfort and convenience. And with the Chrono Package, you can track your lap times and push the limits of your driving skills.

This 911 GT3 is a true enthusiast's dream, offering a level of performance and exclusivity that few can match. With its impeccable condition, striking appearance, and uncompromising Porsche heritage, it's a sports car that will inspire you to push the boundaries of what's possible. Experience the thrill of ownership and schedule a test drive today.

description: The 2013 Ford Focus ST is a sporty and versatile hatchback that delivers an engaging driving experience with practical features for everyday use. Powered by a turbocharged 2.0-liter EcoBoost engine paired with a precise six-speed manual transmission, the Focus ST offers responsive acceleration and confident handling, making it a favorite among driving enthusiasts. Its aggressive styling is complemented by functional fog lights that enhance visibility in poor weather conditions, while tasteful aerodynamic accents emphasize its performance-oriented design. Inside, the cabin offers comfortable seating, a driver-focused layout, and supportive sport seats that keep passengers secure during spirited drives. This particular Focus ST comes well-equipped with modern conveniences and safety features for added comfort and peace of mind. Bluetooth connectivity ensures hands-free calling and seamless audio streaming, while the push-button start and keyless entry system add a level of convenience typically found in higher-end models. Safety is further enhanced by side impact airbags that provide added protection in the event of a collision. Whether you're commuting through the city or carving through winding roads, the 2013 Ford Focus ST offers a unique blend of technology, style, and performance that stands out in the compact car segment. It remains a compelling choice for those who seek a fun-to-drive vehicle without sacrificing practicality.

Discover the exceptional 2022 Toyota Sienna XSE Hybrid, a versatile and well-equipped minivan that seamlessly blends style, technology, and uncompromising performance. With its sleek black exterior and a host of premium features, this Sienna is poised to elevate your driving experience.

Highlighted by its impressive list of amenities, the 2022 Sienna XSE Hybrid offers:

• Blind-Spot Monitors
• Radio: Premium JBL Audio with Navigation
• Front and Rear Dual-Zone Climate Control
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Power Moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Lane Departure Warning System
• Rear Parking Camera
• Adaptive Cruise Control
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto Integration
• Heated Front Seats

Powered by a 2.5L I4 engine and equipped with a seamless CVT transmission, this Sienna delivers an exceptional 36 MPG in the city and on the highway, making it an economical and environmentally conscious choice.

Beyond its impressive performance and efficiency, the Sienna XSE showcases a wealth of advanced safety technologies to give you and your loved ones peace of mind. Features like Automatic High Beams, Brake Assist, and Electronic Stability Control work tirelessly to help keep you secure on the road.

Slip into the premium SofTex-trimmed seats and experience the comfort and refinement that set this Sienna apart. The spacious and versatile interior offers ample room for passengers and cargo, with a split-folding third-row seat and power-adjustable front seats for enhanced flexibility.

Connectivity is key in the modern world, and the Sienna XSE delivers with its state-of-the-art infotainment system. Enjoy seamless integration with your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, as well as a premium JBL audio system to elevate your driving soundtrack.

Whether you're embarking on family adventures, tackling daily errands, or simply seeking a sophisticated and capable minivan, the 2022 Toyota Sienna XSE is the perfect choice. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional vehicle.

Discover the joy of driving with this exceptional 2019 MINI Cooper Classic. This captivating vehicle combines style, performance, and unparalleled craftsmanship, making it the perfect choice for the discerning driver.

• Panoramic Moonroof
• Comfort Access Keyless Entry
• Automatic Climate Control
• Heated Front Seats
• 6-Speed Automatic Transmission with STEPTRONIC

The MINI Cooper Classic's sleek gray exterior and striking alloy wheels create a bold, eye-catching presence on the road. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a sophisticated, well-appointed cabin that showcases MINI's commitment to quality and attention to detail.

Powered by a 1.5L 12V TwinPower Turbo engine, this MINI delivers an exhilarating driving experience with impressive fuel efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 27 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway, you can enjoy the thrill of the open road without breaking the bank.

Convenience and connectivity are at the heart of this MINI Cooper Classic. The Comfort Access Keyless Entry system allows you to effortlessly access your vehicle, while the MINI Excitement Package and MINI Connected technology keep you entertained and informed on every journey.

For added comfort and style, this MINI is equipped with a Panoramic Moonroof, Heated Front Seats, and a sleek Piano Black Interior Surface. The 6-Speed Automatic Transmission with STEPTRONIC ensures a smooth, responsive ride, giving you complete control over your driving experience.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like ABS brakes, Traction Control, and Electronic Stability Control providing the confidence you need on the road. The Emergency Communication System and Low Tire Pressure Warning further enhance your peace of mind.

Discover the perfect balance of performance, efficiency, and sophistication with this 2019 MINI Cooper Classic. Visit our showroom today and experience the thrill of driving this exceptional vehicle for yourself.

As a result, the trade value or selling price you will get for this vehicle is likely to be lower than for a similar vehicle that was not reacquired. This is reflected in the price you are paying for the vehicle now and why the vehicle is less expensive than a similar one that was not reacquired. In time, the difference in value between this vehicle and a normal vehicle will shrink. Therefore, if you plan to keep the vehicle for an extended period of time you will likely capture more of the savings of the lower price than if you sell or trade the vehicle within a short period after purchasing it. This 2019 Nissan Rogue SL FWD in Pearl White Tri‑Coat delivers a premium blend of comfort, technology, and advanced safety features. Powered by a 2.5‑liter 4‑cylinder engine paired with Nissan’s smooth Xtronic CVT, it offers excellent efficiency and everyday drivability. The SL trim elevates the experience with leather‑appointed seating, heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a premium Bose audio system. The panoramic moonroof, 19" alloy wheels, and upscale exterior accents give the Rogue a refined, modern look. Inside, the Almond interior provides a warm, inviting cabin with intuitive technology, including Nissan Door‑to‑Door Navigation, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and NissanConnect Services. Safety is a standout with Nissan’s full suite of driver‑assist features—ProPILOT Assist, Intelligent Cruise Control, Automatic Emergency Braking, Blind Spot Warning, Rear Cross Traffic Alert, and the Intelligent Around View Monitor for 360° visibility. With its comfort, efficiency, and advanced safety technology, the Rogue SL remains one of the most well‑rounded compact SUVs on the road.

description:
Discover the ultimate driving experience with this meticulously maintained 2022 Ram 1500 Laramie. This powerful and versatile truck is ready to elevate your every adventure, offering a seamless blend of capability, comfort, and cutting-edge technology.

• Clean CarFax
• HEMI 5.7L V8 Engine with eTorque
• Leather-Trimmed Bucket Seats
• Upgraded Floor Console
• Mopar Front & Rear Rubber Floor Mats

Boasting a striking white exterior, this Ram 1500 Laramie commands attention on the road. Under the hood, the legendary HEMI 5.7L V8 engine with eTorque delivers an exceptional balance of power and efficiency, ensuring you'll conquer any task with ease. The 8-speed automatic transmission and rear-wheel-drive configuration provide a smooth and responsive driving experience, whether you're navigating city streets or tackling off-road adventures.

Step inside this well-appointed cabin and you'll be greeted by a wealth of premium features that elevate your daily commute. Sink into the luxurious leather-trimmed bucket seats, which offer both heating and ventilation for year-round comfort. The Uconnect 5 infotainment system with an 8.4-inch touchscreen display keeps you connected and entertained, seamlessly integrating with your smartphone via Apple CarPlay and Android Auto.

Enjoy the convenience of dual-zone automatic climate control, a heated steering wheel, and a power-adjustable driver's seat with memory function. The ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera and a suite of advanced safety technologies, including Electronic Stability Control and Brake Assist, provide added peace of mind on the road.

This 2022 Ram 1500 Laramie is a true standout in its class, blending rugged capability with refined sophistication. With its impressive performance, cutting-edge technology, and exceptional comfort, it's the perfect companion for your next adventure. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the exceptional value and uncompromising quality of this remarkable truck.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of power, capability, and modern convenience in the 2017 Nissan Titan SV. This impressive full-size pickup boasts a commanding 5.6L V8 engine and a robust 7-speed automatic transmission, delivering the performance you demand. With its impressive 21 MPG highway fuel efficiency, the Titan SV offers the perfect balance of strength and efficiency.

Elevate your driving experience with this well-equipped Titan SV. Standout features include:

• CLEAN CARFAX WITH NO ACCIDENTS REPORTED
• BLUETOOTH HANDS-FREE CELL PHONE
• NAVIGATION/GPS
• BLIND-SPOT COLLISION MONITOR
• REAR BACK-UP CAMERA
• RUNNING BOARDS
• TRAILER TOW PACKAGE

The SV Comfort & Convenience Package takes this Titan to the next level, adding automatic headlights, rearview monitor, leather-wrapped steering wheel, step rails, body-color rear bumper, chrome interior door locks, front and rear parking sensors, and the advanced NissanConnect infotainment system with navigation, mobile apps, and voice recognition.

Slip into the Titan SV's heated front captain's chairs and enjoy the comfort of dual-zone automatic climate control, a power-adjustable driver's seat, and a premium audio system. The intelligent key system and power sliding rear window add convenience, while the blind spot warning and rear cross-traffic alert systems provide added peace of mind.

Whether you're tackling tough jobs or enjoying the open road, the 2017 Nissan Titan SV delivers the perfect blend of capability, technology, and comfort. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

description:
2019 Mercedes-Benz AMG E63 S 4MATIC+ Sedan

Exterior: Obsidian Black Metallic
Interior: Black Leather

Performance & Drivetrain:
Handcrafted AMG 4.0L V8 biturbo engine paired with the AMG SPEEDSHIFT MCT 9-speed automatic transmission and 4MATIC+ all-wheel drive. Features include AMG Dynamic Engine Mounts, AMG Electronic Rear Limited-Slip Differential, AMG DYNAMIC SELECT drive modes, AMG performance exhaust system, AMG sport suspension with AIR BODY CONTROL, and increased top speed capability up to 186 mph.

Safety & Driver Assistance:
Driver Assistance Package with DISTRONIC PLUS adaptive cruise control, steering assist, route-based speed adaptation, speed limit assist, active parking assist with surround-view camera, PRE-SAFE system, blind spot monitoring, lane keeping assist, front knee airbag, side airbags, tire pressure monitoring system, rearview and surround-view cameras, anti-theft alarm system, and intelligent high-beam control.

Interior:
Heated and ventilated power front seats with memory and lumbar support, AMG Nappa leather interior accents, Nappa leather dashboard, AMG performance steering wheel with shift paddles, Burmester High-End 3D surround sound system, 12.3-inch digital instrument cluster, head-up display, COMAND navigation with live traffic, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, wireless charging, ambient and premium interior lighting, 3-zone automatic climate control, Air Balance cabin fragrance system, soft-close doors, panoramic sunroof, garage door opener, remote start, AMG illuminated door sills, AMG floor mats, and black piano lacquer interior trim.

Exterior Highlights:
AMG wide-body exterior, AMG exterior components, rear spoiler, 20-inch AMG twin 5-spoke wheels with black accents, high-performance summer tires, LED full lighting package with active curve illumination, intelligent high beams, power-folding mirrors with auto-dimming, power rear-window sunshade, manual rear door sunshades, silver seat belts, wheel locking bolts, and AMG crest LED door projectors.

Experience the future of eco-friendly driving with the 2024 Toyota Prius LE. This sleek and sophisticated hybrid sedan boasts impressive fuel efficiency, cutting-edge technology, and a host of premium features that elevate your driving experience.

Packed with desirable amenities, this Prius LE stands out with:
• 6 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Radio data system
• Radio: Audio System
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Rear window defroster
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls

Engineered for exceptional performance, the Prius LE is equipped with a 2.0L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT engine paired with a Continuously Variable (ECVT) transmission, delivering an outstanding 57 MPG in the city and 56 MPG on the highway. This remarkable fuel efficiency not only saves you money at the pump but also reduces your carbon footprint, making it the ideal choice for the environmentally conscious driver.

Designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, the Prius LE boasts a host of advanced features, including a four-wheel independent suspension, traction control, and 4-Wheel Disc Brakes with ABS. The exterior showcases a sleek, modern aesthetic with body-color bumpers, heated power door mirrors, and 17" alloy wheels with covers, while the interior pampers you with a split-folding rear seat, front bucket seats, and a telescoping steering wheel.

Safety is a top priority in the Prius LE, which comes equipped with dual front impact airbags, dual front side impact airbags, an overhead airbag, and an emergency communication system. Additionally, the vehicle features a rear-view camera, auto high-beam headlights, and a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies to help keep you and your passengers secure on the road.

Experience the future of sustainable, high-tech driving with the 2024 Toyota Prius LE. Visit our showroom today to take this exceptional hybrid sedan for a test drive and discover how it can transform your daily commute and your environmental impact.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2012 Ford F-350SD Lariat. Boasting a powerful 6.7L V8 Diesel Turbocharged engine, this truck delivers unparalleled performance and capability. Equipped with a TorqShift 6-Speed Automatic transmission and 4-Wheel Drive, it's ready to tackle any terrain with confidence.

Highlighted features include:
• 6.7L V8 Diesel Turbocharged (Power Stroke) engine
• Chrome Package with 18" chrome clad wheels, bright metallic exhaust tip, and more
• Power Sliding Moonroof with map lights and switches
• Lariat Interior Package with rear view camera, power heated/cooled front seats, and more
• 3.31 Axle Ratio with Electronic Locking Rear Axle
• Tailgate Step with TailGate Assist
• 5th Wheel/Gooseneck Hitch Prep Package
• FX4 Off-Road Package with hill descent control and skid plates

This F-350SD Lariat is built to handle the toughest jobs with ease. The powerful 6.7L V8 Diesel Turbocharged engine provides exceptional towing and hauling capabilities, while the 4-Wheel Drive system ensures you can conquer any terrain. The Chrome Package adds a touch of style and sophistication, while the Lariat Interior Package offers unparalleled comfort and convenience.

Designed with the discerning driver in mind, this F-350SD Lariat is equipped with a host of premium features, including a power sliding moonroof, heated and cooled front seats, and a rear-view camera. The 5th Wheel/Gooseneck Hitch Prep Package and FX4 Off-Road Package further enhance the vehicle's versatility and capability, making it the ideal choice for those who demand the best.

With its impressive performance, robust design, and exceptional features, this 2012 Ford F-350SD Lariat is a true workhorse that will exceed your expectations. Experience the power and refinement of this exceptional truck for yourself. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover the difference.

description:
The 2015 Chrysler 200 C offers a sophisticated blend of sleek style and modern efficiency, finished in a striking Velvet Red Pearlcoat exterior. Powered by the advanced 2.4L I4 MultiAir engine delivering 184 horsepower and 173 lb-ft of torque, this refined sedan provides smooth, responsive performance for the daily drive through its state-of-the-art 9-speed automatic transmission and confident front-wheel drive.

The premium 200 C trim outfits the sedan with 19-inch aluminum wheels, all-season touring tires, and signature LED lighting accents. Inside, you'll find premium leather seating surfaces with heated front seats, a leather-wrapped steering wheel with audio controls, and elegant gloss-black interior accents. The well-appointed cabin offers a spacious trunk for gear, along with dual-zone automatic climate control and a 6-speaker premium audio system for every commute.

Advanced technology features include the intuitive Uconnect infotainment system with an 8.4-inch touchscreen, voice command, and available SiriusXM Satellite Radio. The 200 C also boasts a class-exclusive rotary shifter, available all-speed traction control, and Chrysler's ParkView rear backup camera with dynamic grid lines for enhanced control and confidence in any parking situation.

Engineered for both elegance and everyday practicality, this Chrysler 200 achieves an EPA-estimated 23 MPG city/36 MPG highway, making it an efficient and enjoyable choice for the discerning driver.

- Unmatched Transparency: Prior to your purchase, gain full visibility into the service history of the vehicle, ensuring complete transparency and confidence in your decision.

- Our Best Price Upfront: We recognize the extensive research done by shoppers, hence we offer highly competitive prices online to match your needs and expectations.

- Express Checkout for Time Efficiency: Streamline your purchase process by completing most of the deal remotely, whether from the comfort of your workplace or home, saving you valuable time.

This 2017 Audi A4 allroad 2.0T Premium quattro is a sophisticated and capable crossover that blends the refined driving dynamics of a luxury sedan with the versatility of an SUV. Finished in a sleek Monsoon Gray Metallic exterior, this A4 allroad exudes an elegant and understated presence that is sure to turn heads.

Under the hood, the turbocharged 2.0-liter TFSI engine delivers a potent 252 horsepower, effortlessly channeled through the smooth-shifting 7-speed S tronic transmission and Audi's renowned quattro all-wheel-drive system. With an EPA-estimated 23 mpg city and 28 mpg highway, this A4 allroad provides an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency.

The well-appointed interior is adorned with premium Dark Brown Walnut High Gloss inlays, further enhancing the vehicle's refined ambiance. Heated front seats with driver memory ensure maximum comfort, while the Audi MMI Navigation Plus system with MMI Touch provides seamless connectivity and intuitive control of the vehicle's advanced features.

Convenience is a hallmark of this A4 allroad, thanks to the Convenience Package that includes a power liftgate, Audi Advanced Key for keyless entry and ignition, and a premium Audi Sound System. The Audi Connect PRIME and PLUS features provide a wealth of connected services, from real-time traffic updates to in-car Wi-Fi for on-the-go productivity and entertainment.

Whether tackling the daily commute or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2017 Audi A4 allroad 2.0T Premium quattro is a versatile and refined companion that will exceed your expectations. Experience the difference that Audi's legendary engineering and attention to detail can make in your driving experience.

description:
Discover the power and capability of this 2015 Ram 1500 Big Horn. Boasting a rugged HEMI 5.7L V8 engine with Multi Displacement VVT, this truck delivers impressive performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 22 MPG on the highway. Paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, this Ram 1500 provides a smooth, responsive driving experience whether hauling heavy loads or navigating city streets.

Key features of this well-equipped Big Horn model include:

• Quick Order Package 26Z Big Horn
• Rear Camera & Park Assist Group
• Remote Start & Security Group
• Trailer Tow Mirrors & Brake Group
• Uconnect 8.4A AM/FM/SXM/BT radio with 8.4" touchscreen display
• Premium cloth bucket seats with power lumbar support
• Spray-in bedliner
• Remote start system
• Security alarm

This Ram 1500 also boasts a host of advanced safety and convenience technologies, including ParkSense front and rear park assist, ParkView rear backup camera, and a suite of airbags for comprehensive protection.

With its rugged good looks, impressive capabilities, and well-appointed interior, this 2015 Ram 1500 Big Horn is the perfect choice for drivers seeking a versatile and capable full-size pickup. Whether you're hauling equipment, towing a trailer, or simply enjoying the daily commute, this truck is ready to take on any challenge with confidence and style.

We invite you to come experience the power and refinement of this exceptional Ram 1500 for yourself. Our knowledgeable sales team is standing by to answer any questions you may have and help you discover why this truck may be the perfect fit for your lifestyle. Visit us today and let's discuss how this Ram 1500 Big Horn can exceed your expectations.

description:
This used 2023 Nissan Altima 2.5 SL is a sleek and sophisticated sedan that combines style, comfort, and technology to elevate your driving experience. With its striking Super Black exterior and Light Gray interior, this vehicle exudes a refined presence on the road. Despite being a used model with 62,767 miles, it offers a host of premium features like adaptive cruise control, Apple CarPlay, and a premium audio system that make every journey enjoyable. The Altimas efficient 2.5-liter four-cylinder engine delivers 188 horsepower, paired with a smooth 1-speed CVT transmission, ensuring responsive performance and excellent fuel economy of up to 37 mpg highway. Its spacious four-door design comfortably seats five, making it an ideal choice for daily commutes or longer road trips, all while providing the convenience of keyless entry, push start, and a sunroof to enhance your driving pleasure.

This used Nissan Altima is equipped with advanced safety and driver-assist features to keep you confident behind the wheel. It includes automatic emergency braking with rear collision warning, rear parking sensors, and a rearview camera that provide comprehensive situational awareness. The vehicle also features dual knee airbags, electronic parking brake with auto off, and traffic sign recognition to help you stay aware of your surroundings. Anti-lock brakes, cornering brake control, auto-locking power door locks, and rear check seat reminder further enhance security and convenience. With these safety measures integrated seamlessly into the Altimas design, you can enjoy peace of mind knowing that your vehicle is equipped to handle various driving conditions.

2023 Nissan Altima Safety and Security Features
The safety and security of this used Altima are prioritized with a robust suite of features. It boasts automatic emergency braking for rear collisions, rear parking sensors, and a comprehensive airbag system including dual knee airbags for added protection. Traffic sign recognition helps you stay informed of road regulations, while electronic parking brake with auto off ensures ease of parking. The vehicles anti-lock braking system and cornering brake control enhance stability during sudden stops or turns. Power door locks with auto-locking and anti-lockout functions, along with a rear check seat reminder, provide added security for all passengers, making this Altima as safe as it is stylish.

2023 Nissan Altima Entertainment and Technology Features
This used Nissan Altima offers an impressive array of entertainment and technology options designed to keep you connected and entertained. The centerpiece is a 12.3-inch infotainment touchscreen, which integrates navigation with DVD capability for seamless route guidance. NissanConnect ensures smart device app compatibility, including Google Assistant, allowing you to control various functions via voice commands. Hands-free phone calls and voice-operated radio add to the convenience. The sound system features seven speakers, including two subwoofers, HD radio, and a touch screen display, delivering crisp audio quality. Whether streaming music, navigating unfamiliar roads, or enjoying your favorite radio stations, this Altimas tech features provide a modern, engaging driving environment.

Introducing the all-new 2023 Kia K5 GT-Line, the ultimate combination of style, performance, and technology. This sleek sedan is the perfect blend of athleticism and sophistication, designed to turn heads and elevate your driving experience. With its bold lines and aggressive stance, the K5 GT-Line exudes confidence and demands attention.

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful 1.6L turbocharged engine, delivering an impressive 290 horsepower and 311 lb-ft of torque. Paired with an 8-speed dual-clutch transmission, this car offers exhilarating acceleration and smooth shifting for a thrilling ride every time.
