The ergonomic cockpit puts everything at your fingertips, while the 10.25-inch touchscreen display provides seamless access to navigation, music, and more. And with the available panoramic sunroof, you can bring the outdoors in for a truly immersive driving experience.

Safety is always a top priority in the K5 GT-Line, with advanced features such as forward collision-avoidance assist, lane keeping assist, and blind spot collision-avoidance assist. Plus, with Kia's industry-leading warranty, you can have peace of mind knowing your K5 is backed by 10 years or 100,000 miles of coverage.

Don't settle for ordinary, elevate your driving experience with the 2023 Kia K5 GT-Line. Visit your nearest dealership today and experience the power, style, and technology of this exceptional sedan. With its extra spacing, the K5 GT-Line will give you the space to make your mark on the road.

description: Performance & Capability3.4L Twin-Turbo V6 Engine smooth power delivery with strong torque. 10-Speed Automatic Transmission refined shifting and responsive acceleration. Full-Time 4WD System excellent traction in all conditions. F SPORT-Tuned Adaptive Variable Suspension sport-oriented ride and handling balance. Torsen Limited-Slip Differential (LSD) optimized rear traction for spirited driving. LexusPerformance Dampers & Rear Stabilizer improved body control and agile response. Multi-Terrain Select & Crawl Control multiple terrain modes for off-road confidence. Adaptive Height Control (AHC) automatic ride height adjustment for comfort and clearance. Exterior FeaturesExclusive F SPORT Styling aggressive front/rear fascias and athletic stance. 22 Forged Aluminum Wheels (Dark Gray Finish) signature F SPORT wheel design. Mesh Spindle Grille with Jet-Black Frame bold and distinctive Lexus look. Triple-Beam LED Headlamps & LED Tail Lamps bright and modern lighting. Power Moonroof / Roof Rails enhances openness and utility. Power Rear Door with Kick Sensor hands-free cargo access. Headlamp Washers & Windshield Wiper De-icer visibility support in poor conditions. Interior Comfort & MaterialsSemi-Aniline Leather-Trimmed Seats premium comfort for all passengers. F SPORT Unique Seats with Extra Bolstering supportive during dynamic driving. Heated & Ventilated Front Seats comfort across seasons. Heated Second-Row Outboard Seats & Manual Rear Sunshades added rear comfort. 4-Zone Climate Concierge individualized temperature control for every row. Cool Box & Wireless Phone Charger convenient storage & charging. Thematic Ambient Illumination & Illuminated Door Sills elevated cabin ambiance. Power Tilt-and-Telescopic Steering Column & Heated Leather Steering Wheel driver comfort and command. Digital Rearview Mirror with HomeLink improved rear visibility & integrated garage control. Infotainment & Connectivity12.3 Lexus Interface Touchscreen central hub for navigation and media. Wireless Apple CarPlay & Android Auto smartphone integration. Premium Audio System (Mark Levinson available) world-class sound quality (25-speaker option). Panoramic & Multi-Terrain Monitor with 4 Cameras comprehensive exterior viewing. Heads-Up Display (HUD) crucial driving info projected in drivers line of sight. Safety & Driver AssistanceLexus Safety System+ Suite advanced driver-assist features (PCS, AEB, lane assist, adaptive cruise). Blind Spot Monitor & Rear Cross Traffic Alert added situational awareness. Parking Sensors / Assist & 360-Degree Camera System helps with tight spots. Utility & Practical FeaturesSeating for Seven Adults three-row configuration with power fold-flat third row. Up to 8,000-lb Towing Capacity capable haul power for trailers/boats.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera with washer - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. Even if there are sloppy conditions, the washer keeps the camera's view clean. Rear camera with washer is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description: Experience the perfect blend of luxury, performance, and advanced technology with this 2021 Acura TLX w/Tech. Draped in striking Apex Blue Pearl, this used sedan offers a sophisticated look paired with a comfortable Ebony interior. With only 57,901 miles, it’s a well-maintained vehicle that combines sporty elegance with everyday practicality. Powered by a turbocharged 2.0-liter four-cylinder engine producing 272 horsepower and 280 lb-ft of torque, this front-wheel-drive sedan delivers an engaging drive with impressive fuel efficiency of 22 mpg city and 31 mpg highway. Its sleek four-door design seats five passengers comfortably, making it ideal for both daily commuting and spirited weekend drives. Loaded with premium features, this Acura TLX w/Tech ensures you stay connected and safe on the road. It comes equipped with adaptive cruise control, lane keep assist, and collision warning to enhance safety and driving confidence. The vehicle’s interior boasts heated seats, memory seat settings, a sunroof/moonroof, and keyless entry for added convenience. Modern connectivity is at your fingertips with Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, satellite radio readiness, and a WiFi hotspot, while the premium audio system with 11 speakers and a 10.2-inch infotainment screen provide an immersive entertainment experience. Navigation, a backup camera, blind spot monitor, cross traffic alert, and premium sound round out the comprehensive package designed to elevate your driving experience. 2021 Acura TLX Safety and Security Features This Acura TLX prioritizes your safety with dual front knee airbags and comprehensive safety systems. Traffic sign recognition helps you stay aware of road conditions, while front and rear parking sensors assist with precise maneuvers. The vehicle is equipped with four-wheel ABS, auto-locking power door locks, and an electronic parking brake with auto-off for added control. Cornering brake control enhances stability during turns, and anti-lockout features prevent lockouts, ensuring peace of mind in all driving situations. 2021 Acura TLX Entertainment and Technology Features Stay entertained and connected with an array of advanced technology features, including AcuraLink and Amazon Alexa compatibility. The sound system boasts 11 speakers and a subwoofer, all coordinated through a high-resolution 10.2-inch infotainment screen. Voice-operated hands-free calling and radio functionality make communication and media access effortless. The system supports HD radio and surround sound in 5.1 channels, delivering an immersive audio experience. Additional smart device app functions include engine start, ensuring seamless integration of your digital lifestyle. 2021 Acura TLX Performance Features The Acura TLX w/Tech is equipped with auto start/stop technology, optimizing fuel efficiency and reducing emissions during city driving. This feature automatically turns off the engine when the vehicle is stationary and restarts it seamlessly when you’re ready to move again. This intelligent system contributes to the vehicle’s overall performance, making it an economical yet sporty choice for discerning drivers.

Vehicle Details
Discover exceptional value with this 2021 Honda Civic LX, a reliable and fuel-efficient compact sedan located in Muskogee, OK. With just 30,834 miles on the odometer and powered by a responsive 4-cylinder 2.0L gasoline engine, this Honda Civic delivers a comfortable driving experience and excellent fuel economy—ideal for daily commuting or weekend getaways. This Honda Civic LX is loaded with practical features that enhance safety, convenience, and comfort. Stay connected on the road with Hands Free Bluetooth for seamless phone calls and audio streaming. Navigate tight parking spots confidently using the Back-Up Camera. Automatic Climate Control maintains a comfortable cabin temperature without constant adjustments, while Adaptive Cruise Control helps reduce driver fatigue on highway trips by maintaining a set following distance from traffic. The clean interior and low mileage make this 2021 Honda Civic LX a smart choice for budget-conscious buyers seeking long-term reliability. Regular maintenance and Honda's dependable engineering contribute to its strong resale value. Priced competitively, this vehicle offers the best price in the area for comparable models — an outstanding opportunity for buyers in and around Muskogee, OK. Contact us to schedule a test drive or request additional photos and vehicle history. Don't miss this chance to own a well-equipped, efficient 2021 Honda Civic LX at an unbeatable price.

Equipment
This Honda Civic offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. See what's behind you with the back up camera on this unit. The vehicle has automated speed control that adjusts to maintain a safe following distance, enhancing highway driving convenience. Bluetooth technology is built into the Honda Civic, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. Maintaining a stable interior temperature in the vehicle is easy with the climate control system. The vehicle has a 4 Cyl, 2.0L high output engine. Front wheel drive on this unit gives you better traction and better fuel economy. This model gleams with an elegant silver clear coated finish. The vehicle has an automatic transmission. The Electronic Stability Control will keep you on your intended path. It is equipped with a gasoline engine. The vehicle features cruise control for long trips. Small and nimble the vehicle scoots through traffic. It offers great fuel mileage and ease of parking.

description: This 2017 Ford F-350 Lariat *Lifted* is a bold, capable, and luxurious heavy-duty truck designed to deliver top-tier performance on and off the road. Packed with premium features and rugged enhancements, this F-350 offers a perfect blend of power and refinement. Dominated by its FX4 Off-Road Package and 3.55 Electronic Locking Axle Ratio, it's built for serious terrain. The Skid Plate Package, rear Wheel Well Liners, and front and rear Splash Guards/Mud Flaps provide extra protection wherever you go. Riding on 20-inch Bright Machined Cast Aluminum Wheels wrapped in LT275/65R20E OWL All-Terrain Tires, this lifted truck doesn't just perform—it demands attention. Dual Extra Heavy Duty Alternators, a Tailgate Step, LED Box Lighting, and Upfitter Switches make this a workhorse ready for any task. Inside, the Lariat Ultimate Package takes comfort to the next level with leather-trimmed 40/20/40 split bench seating, heated and cooled seats, and premium audio. The Twin Panel Panoramic Moonroof floods the cabin with natural light, adding a premium touch to every drive. Stay connected and in control with the Voice-Activated Navigation System, Blind Spot Information System with Cross-Traffic Alert, Remote Vehicle Start, and all-weather floor mats for added convenience in every season. This F-350 offers a 6.8 Ft. short bed, 50-state emissions compliance, and is outfitted for utility and luxury alike. Whether you're tackling job sites or weekend adventures, this lifted F-350 Lariat delivers unmatched performance, advanced technology, and rugged presence in one impressive package.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a wealth of premium features, including a power moonroof, heated front seats, and the Subaru STARLINK 8.0" Multimedia Plus system with smartphone integration. The spacious cabin and 60/40 split-folding rear seats provide ample room for passengers and cargo, making this Crosstrek ideal for your next adventure.

description: The 2017 Ford Explorer XLT offers a well-rounded blend of comfort, capability, and modern features, making it an ideal SUV for families and active lifestyles alike. This particular model comes equipped with the sought-after Equipment Group 202A, enhancing both its appearance and functionality. Inside, premium leather seats provide a touch of luxury, while the third-row seating expands passenger capacity, allowing up to seven occupants to travel in comfort. The automatic climate control system and rear A/C ensure everyone stays comfortable, no matter the seating position. For added convenience, the hands-free liftgate allows easy access to the spacious cargo area, even when your hands are full. Technology and practicality converge with features like a backup camera for easier parking and maneuvering, along with a cargo mat and cargo shade to protect and organize your belongings. The California Emissions System ensures compliance with strict environmental standards, making the vehicle suitable for registration in emissions-regulated states. The inclusion of a license plate bracket adds styling and convenience without the need for aftermarket modifications. Whether you're driving around town or heading out on a long road trip, the 2017 Ford Explorer XLT delivers a smooth, confident ride with thoughtful amenities that make daily use more enjoyable. Its versatile design and loaded feature set make it a dependable option for those in need of space, performance, and modern creature comforts.

At Stivers Ford South of Union City, we are dedicated to providing an exceptional Car-Buying experience that goes beyond just selling vehicles. Our commitment to offering the best prices is reflected in our motto: Price Sells Cars. When you choose Stivers Ford South, you’re not only getting a great deal, but also access to unparalleled convenience and service. We offer a 100% online and remote purchase option, allowing you to complete the entire buying process from the comfort of your home. Once you have made your purchase, our Mobile Service brings expert maintenance and repairs directly to your home or office. Additionally, our concierge pick-up and delivery ensures your vehicle is taken care of without interrupting your day. For added convenience, we provide a fleet of loaner vehicles, so you never have to wait at the dealership while your car is being serviced. At Stivers Ford South of Union City, you are not just buying a vehicle- you are choosing a seamless, customer-focused designed to fit your busy lifestyle. Price sells cars, but our service and convenience set us apart.

Silver 2016 GMC Sierra 2500HD SLT 4x4 5 Passenger - Heavy-duty power with premium GMC comfort.

The 2016 GMC Sierra 2500HD SLT 4x4 delivers exceptional strength, advanced technology, and refined interior comfort. This CARFAX One-Owner, Clean CARFAX truck is equipped with heated leather seats, rear view camera, GPS navigation, tow hitch, remote starter, Bluetooth, AUX, XM/Satellite Radio, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and a rugged 4x4 drivetrain built to handle any terrain.
Perfect for drivers who demand both capability and sophistication, the Sierra 2500HD SLT combines powerful towing performance with luxury-level features.

Schedule your test drive today and experience GMC toughness with a touch of class.

Service Work completed on this vehicle includes: Complete Multi-Point Inspection, Oil & Filter Change, Battery Voltage Test, Tires Inspected, Brake Inspection, Emissions System Check, Professional Detailed Inside and Out, Function Test all Lights, Check the Complete Exhaust System, Cooling System Inspection, Transmission Fluid Inspection, Differential Fluid Inspection, Function Test all Options & Accessories.

We welcome all credit types and accept all trade-ins. Our rates start at 6.99% with no money down for good credit. We are also known for helping those with no credit or bad credit. All our vehicles have a clean title and we have four locations to better serve you. description:
Discover the ultimate off-road companion in this 2020 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara. Boasting a rugged 3.6L V6 engine, 8-speed automatic transmission, and capable 4-wheel drive system, this Wrangler is ready to take you on any adventure. Dressed in a stunning green exterior, this Wrangler Unlimited Sahara is equipped with an impressive array of premium features that will elevate your driving experience.

• MOPAR Black Perforated Leather
• Black 3-Piece Hard Top
• LED Lighting Group
• Cold Weather Group
• Trailer Tow & HD Electrical Group
• 240 Amp Alternator
• 700 Amp Maintenance Free Battery
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Heated Front Seats
• Class II Receiver Hitch
• Wheels: 18" x 7.5" Polished w/Gray Spokes

This Wrangler Unlimited Sahara is more than just a capable off-roader, it's a true expression of your adventurous spirit. The LED lighting, including daytime running lamps, front fog lamps, and reflector headlamps, provide exceptional visibility and a bold, modern look. The Cold Weather Group, featuring heated steering wheel and front seats, ensures you stay comfortable no matter the conditions.

For those with towing needs, the Trailer Tow & HD Electrical Group, complete with a Class II receiver hitch, 7 & 4 pin wiring harness, and 240 Amp alternator, makes this Wrangler a versatile and capable companion. The Anti-Spin Differential Rear Axle provides enhanced traction and control, while the auxiliary switches allow you to easily integrate additional accessories.

Elevate your driving experience with the premium features of this 2020 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sahara. With its exceptional off-road capabilities, advanced technology, and uncompromising comfort, this Wrangler is the perfect choice for those who demand the very best. Schedule a test drive today and discover the true meaning of adventure.

description: The 2014 Chevy Malibu LT is a versatile and stylish midsize sedan that blends comfort, technology, and safety in an attractive package. Its sleek exterior design is complemented by a well-appointed interior, offering ample space for both driver and passengers. The Malibu LT comes equipped with modern conveniences including Bluetooth connectivity, allowing for hands-free phone calls and audio streaming, enhancing both safety and ease of use. The inclusion of keyless entry adds an extra layer of convenience, making it simple to access and start your vehicle quickly without fumbling for keys. Safety is a strong suit in the 2014 Malibu LT, with features such as side impact airbags providing added protection for all occupants in the event of a collision. The sedan is also satellite radio ready, giving drivers access to a wide range of entertainment options on the road, whether commuting or embarking on a long trip. The Malibu LT's quiet cabin, responsive handling, and solid fuel efficiency make it a popular choice among midsize sedans. With a balance of reliable performance, user-friendly technology, and important safety features, the 2014 Chevrolet Malibu LT delivers a comfortable, secure, and enjoyable driving experience for modern drivers.

description: Discover the power and versatility of the 2024 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star. This impressive truck is more than just a workhorse - it's a true companion that can tackle any task with confidence and style.CLEAN CARFAXANDROID AUTOBACK UP CAMERABED LINERWELL MAINTAINED, REGULAR OIL CHANGESHEMI 5.7L V8 Engine with eTorqueBig Horn Level 1 Equipment GroupOff Road GroupRemote Start SystemTrailer Brake ControlE-Locker Rear AxleFront and Rear Extra HD Shock AbsorbersSelec-Speed ControlUnder the hood, the powerful HEMI 5.7L V8 with eTorque technology delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency. With 8-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive, this Ram 1500 is ready to take on any terrain, whether you're hauling a heavy load or embarking on an off-road adventure. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this Ram 1500 is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

description: Recent Arrival! 19/26 City/Highway MPGPantera Metal 2022 Kia Carnival LXS FWD 8-Speed Automatic V6Meet the 2022 Kia Carnival LXS the perfect blend of SUV-style design and minivan versatility, built for families who want space without sacrificing style.This Carnival LXS stands out with its bold, modern exterior and confident stance, giving you the look of a crossover with the functionality you need for everyday life. Under the hood, the powerful and smooth V6 engine delivers confident acceleration while maintaining impressive efficiency for road trips or daily commutes.Inside, the Carnival offers a spacious, thoughtfully designed cabin with comfortable seating for up to eight passengers. Premium cloth seating, a power driver’s seat, tri-zone automatic climate control, and smart storage solutions make every drive more enjoyable. The large touchscreen infotainment system with Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto keeps everyone connected and entertained on the go.Safety is a top priority, and the Carnival LXS delivers with advanced driver-assist features including Forward Collision-Avoidance Assist, Lane Keeping Assist, Blind-Spot Collision-Avoidance Assist, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Smart Cruise Control giving you added confidence behind the wheel.With flexible seating, generous cargo space, modern technology, and standout styling, the 2022 Kia Carnival LXS is ready to handle family life, road trips, and everything in between. Practical, stylish, and dependable this is the minivan reimagined. Ask about available certifications. Used vehicles 10 years of age or newer with less than 100,000 miles are eligible for the Wyler Assurance Program, but eligible vehicles must pass our reconditioning process and multi-point inspection. Provided the vehicle passes inspection, vehicles will be eligible for the 6 month/6,000 mile limited warranty. The 6 month/6,000 mile limited warranty is NOT available on AS-IS vehicles, wholesale vehicles, lease buyback/pass-thru vehicles or un-inspected vehicles. Note that this program can also apply to vehicles where the remaining factory coverage is less than 6 months or 6,000 miles. Please check the Federal Trade Commission (FTC) Buyers guide on the vehicle for full details as to whether or not warranty coverage may apply. Contact Dealer for additional details. The Wyler Assurance 6 month/6,000 Mile limited warranty ends 6 months from the date of the Retail Purchase Agreement (BUYERS ORDER) or when the vehicle's odometer registers 6,000 additional miles to the mileage listed on the BUYERS ORDER, whichever comes first. Vehicle Details
Looking for a stylish, fuel-efficient compact crossover with low miles and exceptional value? This 2021 Kia Soul GT-Line in Taunton, MA delivers. Featuring a peppy 2.0L 4-cylinder gasoline engine with front-wheel drive, this Kia Soul balances spirited everyday driving with impressive fuel economy. With only 21,164 miles on the odometer, this vehicle offers years of dependable service and lower ownership costs compared with higher-mileage alternatives. Inside, the GT-Line trim brings a comfortable, modern cabin loaded with tech: Apple CarPlay and Android Auto keep your smartphone connected for navigation and media, while Hands-Free Bluetooth allows seamless calls and audio streaming. Safety is highlighted by Collision Avoidance technology and a Back-Up Camera for confidence in tight parking situations. The Kia Soul's boxy design provides surprising interior room and versatile cargo capacity, making it practical for commuters, small families, and weekend adventures. This vehicle is being offered at the best price in the area, representing real value for buyers seeking low-mileage, feature-rich transportation in Taunton, MA. Well-maintained and ready for immediate delivery, the 2021 Kia Soul GT-Line is an excellent choice for buyers prioritizing safety features, modern connectivity, and economical performance. Schedule a test drive today and experience this standout compact crossover for yourself.

Equipment
The Kia Soul offers Apple CarPlay for seamless connectivity. Bluetooth technology is built into it, keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. See what's behind you with the back up camera on the Kia Soul. This Kia Soul utilizes collision avoidance to enhance safety by automatically detecting and evading potential accidents. The vehicle comes equipped with Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration on the road. This model excites both driver and bystanders with a polished red exterior with racy lines. This unit features a HomeLink System. This unit has a 4 Cyl, 2.0L high output engine. Set the temperature exactly where you are most comfortable in it. The fan speed and temperature will automatically adjust to maintain your preferred zone climate. Front wheel drive on the Kia Soul gives you better traction and better fuel economy. The high efficiency automatic transmission shifts smoothly and allows you to relax while driving.

Packages
Electrochromic Mirror with Compass and HomeLink. Carpeted Floor Mats. Cargo Net. **Equipment listed is based on original vehicle build and subject to change. Please confirm the accuracy of the included equipment by calling the dealer prior to purchase.**

description:
Discover the Pinnacle of Performance and Sophistication in the 2020 Ford Explorer ST

Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional 2020 Ford Explorer ST. This dynamic SUV combines unparalleled power, cutting-edge technology, and refined style, making it the ultimate choice for those who demand the best.

• Twin Panel Moonroof
• Remote Control Front Windows
• Premium Technology Package with 10.1" LCD Capacitive Portrait Touchscreen and 2 Additional Speakers
• ST Street Pack with 21" Aluminum Wheels, Performance Front & Rear Brakes, and Red Painted Brake Calipers
• Leather Heated and Ventilated Sport Captain's Chairs

Beneath the sculpted exterior, the 2020 Explorer ST delivers a thrilling performance, thanks to its potent 3.0L EcoBoost V6 engine and 10-speed automatic transmission with 4-wheel drive. With an impressive 400 horsepower and 415 lb-ft of torque, this SUV offers the perfect blend of power and efficiency, delivering an EPA-estimated 18 city and 24 highway MPG.

Elevate your driving experience with the cutting-edge technology features of the 2020 Explorer ST. The Premium Technology Package includes a stunning 10.1" LCD Capacitive Portrait Touchscreen, providing intuitive control over your entertainment, navigation, and connectivity needs. Enjoy the rich, immersive sound of the B&O Sound System by Bang & Olufsen, with 12 premium speakers and SiriusXM satellite radio.

Comfort and convenience are paramount in the 2020 Explorer ST. Indulge in the luxurious leather-wrapped, heated and ventilated sport captain's chairs, which offer exceptional support and adjustability. The twin-panel moonroof floods the cabin with natural light, creating a truly open and airy environment.

Designed to impress, the 2020 Ford Explorer ST exudes a bold, athletic presence with its distinctive ST styling cues. The 21" aluminum wheels, performance brakes, and red-painted calipers add a touch of sportiness, while the Star White Metallic Tri-Coat paint finish commands attention wherever you go.

Experience the pinnacle of performance, technology, and style in the 2020 Ford Explorer ST. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional SUV can elevate your driving experience. We're confident that once you take it for a test drive, you'll be captivated by its uncompromising capabilities and refined sophistication.

2020 Kia Forte LXS | Efficient, Reliable, and Smartly Equipped

This 2020 Kia Forte LXS offers modern styling, impressive efficiency, and everyday practicality, making it an excellent choice for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone seeking dependable transportation at an exceptional value. With 81,563 miles, this Forte reflects Kia's reputation for long-term reliability and low cost of ownership.

Powered by a fuel-efficient 2.0L 4-cylinder engine, the Forte delivers smooth performance and confident handling while maintaining excellent fuel economy for daily driving and longer trips. Its responsive steering and comfortable ride make it equally enjoyable in city traffic or on the highway.

Inside, the Forte LXS features a thoughtfully designed cabin with comfortable seating, quality materials, and a clean, modern layout. The interior provides ample legroom for both front and rear passengers, along with a generously sized trunk that offers outstanding cargo versatility for groceries, luggage, or work gear.

Technology and safety are highlights, featuring a touchscreen infotainment system, Bluetooth connectivity, Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, USB ports, and steering-wheel-mounted controls to keep you connected and in control. Kia's advanced safety features include Forward Collision-Avoidance Assist, Lane Keeping Assist, Driver Attention Warning, electronic stability control, and a rearview camera, offering added confidence on every drive.

With its sleek exterior design, refined ride quality, and excellent efficiency, the Forte LXS stands out as a smart and economical compact sedan. If you're searching for a reliable, well-equipped vehicle that delivers comfort, safety, and value, this 2020 Kia Forte LXS is ready to meet your needs.

description: This 1-OWNER 2019 Ford F-150 Raptor SuperCrew is a high-performance, off-road-ready pickup that blends rugged capability with cutting-edge technology and exceptional comfort. Equipped with the sought-after Equipment Group 802A and Raptor Technology Package, this truck boasts features like Adaptive Cruise Control, Lane Keep Assist, Blind Spot Information System with Cross-Traffic Alert, and a 360-Degree Camera for added confidence on any journey. The Raptor's enhanced off-road performance comes courtesy of Fox Shocks along with the 4.10 Electronic Locking Axle Ratio, 4.10 Front Axle with Torsen Differential, and forged aluminum bead-lock capable wheels. With a powerful engine and advanced trail-ready features like the Pro Trailer Backup Assist and Integrated Trailer Brake Controller, the Raptor is built for serious adventure and work capability alike.----Inside the SuperCrew cabin, you'll find premium amenities like richly appointed leather 40/console/40 front seats, a Premium Audio system, and the convenience of a Remote Start System. The Voice-Activated Navigation System, Wi-Fi Hotspot, and Twin Panel Panoramic Moonroof ensure every ride is as connected and enjoyable as it is capable. Functional design continues to the exterior with a 5.5-foot short bed featuring a durable Spray-In Bed Liner, Pickup Box LED Lighting, Tailgate Step, and sleek Raptor Exterior Graphics Package. LED Puddle/Side Mirror Spotlights and power glass, heated side mirrors with integrated turn signals add further convenience and safety. With Inflatable Rear Safety Belts and advanced driver-assist technologies, the 2019 Raptor SuperCrew delivers confidence and performance in a bold, rugged package.

Elevate your driving experience with this 2017 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack TSI SE 4Motion. Step inside the X7 xDrive40i and experience the epitome of comfort and style. The spacious interior boasts premium leather seating, along with ample legroom and headroom for all passengers. The panoramic sunroof allows for natural light to flood the cabin, creating an open and airy atmosphere.

Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2018 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT. This powerful and versatile full-size pickup boasts a remarkable combination of premium features and exceptional performance, making it the perfect choice for those who demand the best.

Highlighted features include:
• SLT Crew Cab Premium Plus Package

Powered by the robust EcoTec3 5.3L V8 engine and equipped with 4-wheel drive, this Sierra 1500 delivers impressive capability and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 16 city/21 highway MPG. The smooth-shifting 8-speed automatic transmission and advanced suspension system ensure a confident and comfortable ride, whether you're navigating city streets or tackling rugged terrain.

The exterior of this Sierra 1500 SLT is finished in a sleek White Frost Tricoat, complemented by chrome accents and bold LED lighting. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed cabin, featuring premium leather-appointed seating, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a wealth of advanced technology and safety features.

Experience the unparalleled capability, comfort, and style of this 2018 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT. Visit our showroom today and let our knowledgeable sales team demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can enhance your driving experience.

description:
Experience the thrill of pure power and performance in this exceptional 2019 Chevrolet Camaro SS 1SS. Boasting a commanding 6.2L V8 engine and a 6-speed manual transmission, this Camaro delivers an exhilarating driving experience that will leave you craving the open road.

Highlighted by the impressive SS 1LE Track Performance Package, this Camaro is equipped with a comprehensive suite of track-focused features, including:

• SS 1LE TRACK PERFORMANCE PACKAGE
• Brembo Red, 6-piston front monobloc calipers and 4-piston rear calipers
• Electronic limited-slip differential
• Magnetic Ride Control suspension
• Performance suspension
• Black front splitter and Satin Black hood wrap
• Satin Black rear blade spoiler
• 20" Satin Graphite forged aluminum wheels
• RECARO performance front bucket seats
• Sueded-wrapped flat-bottom steering wheel and shift knob

In addition to its exceptional performance capabilities, this Camaro also boasts a wealth of premium features, including the Chevrolet Infotainment 3 Plus System, Head-Up Display, and a premium audio system with SiriusXM Radio. The sleek, White exterior and well-appointed interior create a stunning visual package that is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

With its powerful engine, track-tuned suspension, and comprehensive suite of advanced technologies, this 2019 Chevrolet Camaro SS 1SS is the ultimate expression of American muscle car performance. Whether you're carving through winding roads or enjoying a spirited drive on the open highway, this Camaro will deliver an unparalleled driving experience that will leave a lasting impression.

We invite you to experience the thrill of this exceptional Camaro for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate the true capabilities of this remarkable vehicle. With its impressive performance, premium features, and stunning good looks, this Camaro is sure to exceed your expectations and leave you eager to take the wheel.

description:
2019 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT Crew Cab Short Bed – Summit White

This 2019 Chevrolet Silverado 1500 LT Crew Cab delivers classic V8 power, Texas-ready capability, and everyday comfort in a proven full-size pickup. Finished in Summit White with a durable cloth interior, this Silverado is well-equipped for work, towing, and daily driving alike.

Under the hood is the sought-after 5.3L EcoTec3 V8 paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, providing strong performance and confident highway towing. The Texas Edition Package adds valuable upgrades that enhance both capability and comfort.

Key Features & Highlights:

5.3L V8 engine with 8-speed automatic transmission

Texas Edition Package with locking/limited-slip differential

Trailering Package with integrated trailer brake controller

Convenience Package with remote engine start

Heated front seats & heated steering wheel

Power driver seat with lumbar support

Dual-zone automatic climate control with rear air vents

Leather-wrapped steering wheel

Apple CarPlay® & Android Auto™ compatibility

Wi-Fi Hotspot capability

Aluminum wheels and all-season tires

LED cargo area lighting

Rear vision camera

Safety & Technology:

Tire Pressure Monitoring System

Stability & Traction Control

Multiple airbags throughout the cabin

Daytime Running Lights

Integrated hitch guidance for easier trailering

With its roomy crew cab, proven V8 performance, and strong list of comfort and towing features, this Silverado LT is an excellent choice for anyone needing a dependable and versatile truck.

Want a walk-around video or to schedule a test drive? Just say the word — we’ll have it ready and waiting up front.

Big Horn Level 1 Equipment Group
Adds upgraded convenience and technology features, including enhanced connectivity, premium interior touches, and advanced driver-assist systems.

Trailer Tow Group
Provides the towing hardware and technology needed for confident hauling, including integrated trailer brake controller, hitch equipment, and tow-assist features.

Bed Utility Group
Enhances cargo-area functionality with bed lighting, extra utility components, and convenience features designed for work or recreation.

eTorque System
Improves efficiency and performance with Rams mild-hybrid technology, enhancing low-end torque and overall responsiveness.

Comfort & Capability
The Big Horn trim offers a comfortable, well-appointed cabin paired with Rams renowned ride quality, making it ideal for daily driving and weekend work.

Why This Ram 1500 Stands Out
With its combination of desirable equipment groups, towing capability, cargo utility, and modern efficiency, this 2023 Ram 1500 Big Horn RWD is a versatile and high-value pickup ready for work or everyday use.

Discover the power and style of the 2024 Ram 1500 Classic Warlock. This exceptional truck is a true workhorse, built to handle any task with ease and confidence. With its robust 3.6L V6 engine, 8-speed automatic transmission, and 4-wheel drive capabilities, this Warlock is ready to take on any terrain or challenge you throw its way.

- Delmonico Red Pearlcoat exterior in a bold Red color
- Quick Order Package 29F Warlock
- 6 Speakers, AM/FM radio: SiriusXM, Audio Input Jack for Mobile Devices
- GPS Antenna Input, Radio data system, Radio: Uconnect 3 w/5" Display
- Air Conditioning, Power steering, Power windows, Remote keyless entry, Tip Start
- Raised Ride Height, Rear Extra HD Shock Absorbers, Traction control
- 4-Wheel Disc Brakes, ABS brakes, Dual front impact airbags, Dual front side impact airbags
- Front anti-roll bar, Front wheel independent suspension, Low tire pressure warning, Occupant sensing airbag, Overhead airbag, Rear anti-roll bar

The 2024 Ram 1500 Classic Warlock is a true standout, both in performance and style. With its bold Delmonico Red Pearlcoat exterior, rugged Warlock package, and impressive array of features, this truck is ready to take on any challenge. Whether you're tackling tough jobs or seeking a capable and stylish daily driver, the Warlock has everything you need and more.

Boasting an EPA-estimated 16 city/23 highway mpg, the 2024 Ram 1500 Classic Warlock delivers impressive efficiency without sacrificing power. The 3.6L V6 engine and 8-speed automatic transmission provide a smooth and responsive driving experience, while the 4-wheel drive system ensures you can conquer any terrain with confidence.

Inside, the Warlock offers a well-appointed cabin with premium cloth seating, a 40/20/40 split bench seat, and a host of convenience features. Stay connected with the Uconnect 3 system, which includes a 5-inch display, SiriusXM radio, and Bluetooth connectivity. The Warlock also comes equipped with a ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera and ParkSense Rear Park Assist System, making parking and maneuvering a breeze.

Experience the power, style, and capability of the 2024 Ram 1500 Classic Warlock. This exceptional truck is ready to take on your toughest challenges and provide you with a driving experience that is second to none. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Warlock is the perfect choice for your next vehicle.

This vehicle has the following features: Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • AppLink/Apple CarPlay and Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
  • AppLink/Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring

description: The 2018 Toyota Tacoma TRD Sport 4WD is a rugged yet refined midsize pickup designed for drivers who demand both capability and comfort. With its aggressive styling, hood scoop, and signature TRD Sport badging, this Tacoma stands out on the road while delivering serious off-road performance with its four-wheel-drive system. Under the hood, it features a powerful V6 engine paired with a smooth-shifting transmission, providing responsive acceleration and towing strength. The TRD-tuned suspension enhances handling both on and off the pavement, offering a confident and composed ride no matter the terrain. Inside, the Tacoma TRD Sport combines utility with modern luxury. The cabin is equipped with premium leather seats for an upscale feel, while the available sunroof adds a sense of openness and natural light. Technology is front and center, including a premium audio system that delivers crisp, immersive sound on every drive. Drivers will appreciate the integrated navigation system for ease of travel and the advanced suite of driver assistance features such as Adaptive Cruise Control and Collision Warning, contributing to peace of mind behind the wheel. Whether you're navigating city streets or tackling backcountry trails, the 2018 Toyota Tacoma TRD Sport 4WD delivers the perfect balance of performance, style, and innovative features.

This 2022 Nissan Sentra SV is a standout choice for the savvy driver seeking exceptional value and a rewarding driving experience. With its sleek blue exterior, this Sentra boasts a sophisticated style that commands attention on the road. Under the hood, the efficient 2.0L DOHC engine paired with the smooth-shifting CVT transmission delivers an impressive 29 city/39 highway MPG, making it an economical companion for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Step inside, and you'll be greeted by premium cloth seating, a spacious cabin, and a wealth of advanced technologies. The NissanConnect system seamlessly integrates your smartphone, providing access to your favorite apps, music, and navigation. Blind Spot Warning and Auto High-beam Headlights enhance your awareness and confidence behind the wheel, while the Rear Parking Sensors make maneuvering a breeze.

Designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, this Sentra SV comes equipped with a host of thoughtful features, including a Carpeted Floor Mats w/Trunk Mat, Body Colored Splash Guards, and Door Sill Plates. The Split Folding Rear Seat and Front Center Armrest ensure that you and your passengers can travel in comfort, whether you're running errands or embarking on a road trip.

With its exceptional fuel efficiency, comprehensive safety features, and impressive array of amenities, this 2022 Nissan Sentra SV is a testament to Nissan's commitment to delivering a premium driving experience at an exceptional value. We invite you to experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive at Auction Direct Raleigh.

When you shop at Auction Direct Raleigh, you’re choosing a dealership known for transparent pricing, strong value, and a huge inventory of used cars, trucks, and SUVs for every budget. Our customer-focused approach makes us a leading choice for used car shoppers in Raleigh, Durham, Wake Forest, Cary, and the surrounding Triangle communities.

Every vehicle at Auction Direct comes pre-installed with Recovr vehicle location technology and professional window tint, included for a total cost of $799.

The 2022 Ford Escape SE FWD in Carbonized Gray presents a sleek and modern profile that captures the essence of urban sophistication and everyday versatility. With its dynamic exterior, this compact SUV is designed to turn heads, whether you're navigating busy city streets or cruising down the open highway. Its inviting Dark Earth Gray interior complements the exterior harmoniously, offering a refined and comfortable atmosphere for both driver and passengers alike. Under the hood, the Escape SE is powered by a 1.5L EcoBoost engine with three cylinders, delivering a perfect balance of efficiency and spirited performance. This engine configuration ensures a responsive driving experience while optimizing fuel economy for longer journeys and daily commutes. The SE trim includes the Equipment Group 200A, which adds an array of desirable features designed to enhance convenience and driving pleasure, perfectly suiting the needs of today's modern driver. The inclusion of a mini spare wheel provides peace of mind, ensuring that you're prepared for unexpected roadside situations.The Convenience Package elevates the Escape's practicality even further, featuring amenities designed to make every trip more enjoyable and stress-free. The package includes elements that cater to both comfort and utility, adding to the SUV's appeal. Additionally, the front license plate bracket is thoughtfully included, providing practical utility for regions where it’s required. With its perfect blend of style, efficiency, and convenience, the 2022 Ford Escape SE FWD stands as an appealing choice for those seeking a well-rounded compact SUV. description:
The **2022 Volvo XC90 T8 Plug-In Hybrid** is a premium three-row luxury SUV that pairs a turbocharged 2.0-liter engine with an electric motor for a powerful yet efficient plug-in hybrid experience. It offers a combined output of around 400455 horsepower and a focus on Scandinavian design with a refined, tech-rich interior. The T8s plug-in system allows for an EPA-estimated electric-only driving range and strong fuel efficiency compared with conventional large SUVs. Inside, the XC90 blends upscale comfort with advanced safety and tech features like a large touchscreen display, digital driver cluster, and a suite of driver-assist systems. With spacious seating, all-wheel drive capability, and a balance of performance and eco-friendly driving options, the XC90 T8 delivers versatile luxury for families and long-distance journeys.

Every used vehicle on our lot goes through a strenuous, multi-point inspection before its ever offered for sale because quality and safety aren't just priorities for us, they're part of our heritage. Our factory-trained technicians thoroughly examine all major systems, including the engine, transmission, brakes, suspension, tires, and electrical components, to ensure each vehicle meets our high standards for performance and reliability. We also inspect for signs of prior damage, mechanical issues, and cosmetic wear, inside and out. If something doesn't meet our strict criteria, its either repaired or replaced before the vehicle reaches the lot. This careful process reflects our commitment to your peace of mind, you deserve a vehicle you can count on.
That commitment runs deep in our roots. The Jackie Cooper name has proudly served Oklahoma's automotive community since 1946. We are a third-generation, family-owned dealership group that began with my grandfather, Claude Cooper, well known as the best mechanic in Canadian County. He launched our family's journey in the car business by purchasing his first franchise, an Oldsmobile dealership in Yukon, from the local funeral director who, in true small-town fashion, sold cars and conducted funerals in the same building. Yes, really.
After Claude, my father Jackie Cooper took the reins, and our family's dedication to service, honesty, and relationships only grew stronger. We've been part of countless Oklahomans' lives for nearly 80 years, he
If you would like to schedule a VIP appt, please feel free to contact us at 918.806.8548 Helping generations find dependable vehicles and standing by every customer long after the sale.
Like any business, we're not perfect but when we fall short, we make it right. The lessons passed down from my grandfather and father still guide us today: always do the right thing, treat people with respect, and earn trust every single day.
At Jackie Cooper, you're not just buying a used vehicle, you're joining a legacy built on integrity, quality, and care.

Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! What this vehicle includes: Cold Weather Package ($1,050 value)
  • Heated Steering Wheel
  • Heated Front Seats
  • Neck Warmer
  • Retractable Headlight Washers
Driver Assistance Package ($950 value)
  • Rear View Camera
  • Park Distance Control
Driver Assistance Plus ($1,700 value)
  • Active Blind Spot Detection
  • Active Driving Assistant
  • Side and Top View Cameras
  • Speed Limit Information
Premium Package ($2,200 value)
  • Comfort Access Keyless Entry
  • Lumbar Support
  • SiriusXM Satellite Radio
  • Dakota Leather Upholstery
Technology Package ($2,750 value)
  • Navigation System
  • Head-Up Display
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Head-up display - Keep your head up! You don't have to take your eyes off of the road to get information from your dashboard anymore. With head-up display, important driving information - like speed and RPM's - displays on your windshield in your line of sight. Because when you're driving, the most important information lies on the road ahead. Keep your eyes on the road with head-up display.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Internet access - Bring the world into your vehicle. Using the vehicle's onboard internet access, you can access maps, the latest weather updates, and other valuable information to make your drive better. Now you don't have to exhaust your phone's data just because your on the road, thanks to Internet access.
Come on in to BMW of Lafayette today at 178 Sagamore Parkway South Lafayette IN 47905 or call to schedule a test drive!

Introducing the sleek and powerful 2021 Toyota Avalon XSE Nightshade, the ultimate combination of style and performance. This luxurious sedan boasts a 3.5L V6 engine, producing an impressive 301 horsepower and 267 foot-pounds of torque. Equipped with an 8-speed automatic transmission with sequential shift mode, the Avalon XSE Nightshade offers a smooth and responsive driving experience.

But it's not just what's under the hood that sets this vehicle apart. The Nightshade edition adds an extra touch of sophistication with its all-black exterior, featuring black 19-inch alloy wheels, black door handles and mirror caps, and black badging. The bold and aggressive front grille is also finished in black, making a statement wherever you go.

Step inside the 2021 Avalon XSE Nightshade and you'll be greeted with a luxurious and spacious interior. The black SofTex-trimmed seats are accented with blue stitching, creating a striking contrast. The 8-way power-adjustable driver's seat and 4-way power-adjustable passenger seat ensure maximum comfort for every journey.

Loaded with advanced technology, the Avalon XSE Nightshade offers a seamless driving experience. The 9-inch touchscreen display allows you to easily access your favorite apps and features, while the available JBL® Premium Audio system delivers crystal-clear sound. Plus, with features like Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto™ compatibility, you can stay connected and entertained on the go.

Don't miss your chance to own the 2021 Toyota Avalon XSE Nightshade. With its impressive performance, sleek design, and cutting-edge technology, this sedan is sure to turn heads and elevate your driving experience. Visit our dealership today and experience it for yourself.

Elevate your off-road adventures with the exceptional 2025 Toyota 4Runner i-FORCE MAX Hybrid TRD Off Road Premium. This remarkable SUV combines unparalleled capability, advanced technology, and exceptional comfort, making it the ultimate choice for those who demand the best.

• **GETTEL CERTIFIED**90DAY PLATINUM WARRANTY**SEE DEALER FOR DETAILS**
• Navigation System
• 15 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Radio: 14" Audio
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Front dual zone A/C
• Rear window defroster
• Memory seat
• Power driver seat
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Speed-sensing steering
• Traction control

Powered by the innovative 2.4L I4 FI Hybrid Turbocharged DOHC 16V engine and an 8-speed automatic transmission, this 4Runner delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency. With its impressive 23 city/24 highway MPG, you'll enjoy the freedom to explore without sacrificing fuel economy.

As a Toyota Certified Used Hybrid, this 4Runner has undergone a rigorous 160-point inspection and comes with an impressive array of warranty coverage, including a 12-month/12,000-mile limited comprehensive warranty, an 84-month/100,000-mile powertrain limited warranty, and a 10-year/150,000-mile HV battery warranty. With a powerful 2.0-liter Inline-4 engine boasting 255 horsepower, this GLE promises an exhilarating driving experience each time you hit the road.Equipped with standard safety features like Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) and side curtain airbags for the first and second rows, this SUV ensures the protection of its occupants. From the Left-Hand Drive (LHD) steering location, the driver can take control of the road with a smooth 9-speed automatic transmission system.This GLE model offers a balanced mix of performance and efficiency, featuring a Turbocharged engine design and a dual overhead cam (DOHC) valve train configuration. The vehicle's Water cooling system ensures optimal engine temperature management, promoting longevity and reliability.Experience a seamless car-buying journey with Mercedes-Benz of Farmington, offering a transparent and efficient purchasing process that respects your time and needs. description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and versatility in the 2023 Kia Seltos EX. This exceptional crossover SUV is poised to elevate your driving experience with its impressive array of features and capabilities.

Boasting a stunning Blue exterior, the Seltos EX commands attention on the road. Equipped with a 2.0L I4 MPI engine and AWD, this vehicle delivers a thrilling and efficient ride, achieving an impressive 27 MPG in the city and 31 MPG on the highway.

Key features of this Seltos EX include:

• Cross Bars
• Carpet Floor Mats

Beyond these thoughtful additions, the Seltos EX is packed with a wealth of advanced technologies and premium amenities to enhance your daily commute and weekend adventures. Enjoy the convenience of the Navigation System, the clarity of the 6 Speakers, and the seamless integration of Apple CarPlay & Android Auto.

Stay comfortable and in control with features like Automatic Temperature Control, Power Driver Seat, and Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls. The Seltos EX also prioritizes your safety with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including ABS Brakes, Dual Front Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control.

Elevate your driving experience with the Seltos EX's premium Sofino Leatherette Seat Trim, Heated Front Seats, and Power Moonroof. The split-folding rear seat and ample cargo space ensure you can accommodate all your needs, whether it's transporting passengers or hauling gear.

Wrapped in a sleek and modern design, the Seltos EX exudes a sense of sophistication and confidence. Alloy wheels with a Machined Finish and a sporty Spoiler add to the vehicle's dynamic appearance, turning heads wherever you go.

With a list price of just $22,999, the 2023 Kia Seltos EX represents an exceptional value proposition. This crossover SUV delivers a winning combination of style, technology, and performance, making it the ideal choice for discerning buyers seeking a versatile and capable vehicle.

Discover the joy of driving the 2023 Kia Seltos EX. Visit our showroom today and experience the difference for yourself. We're confident you'll be impressed by this remarkable crossover SUV.
